26,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name session-store-ingress, deployed to data. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Specifications include routed through the haproxy ingress class, and bound to host api.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.ingressClassName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""haproxy""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: session-store-ingress
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: rate-limiter
spec:
  rules:
  - host: api.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /static
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: event-bus-svc
            port:
              number: 443
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - api.example.com
    secretName: session-store-tls
  ingressClassName: haproxy",Ingress,5
27,"Please configure a Pod identified as model-trainer-pod within monitoring. Make sure it has carrying the app=model-trainer label, and based on the golang:3.1 image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:3.1""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: model-trainer-pod
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: model-trainer
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: runner
    image: golang:3.1
    imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent",Pod,5
28,"We need a ConfigMap named audit-logger-config in data. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. The configuration requires including a feature_flags data key, and also containing the retry_count entry, additionally mapping retry_count to 10, containing feature_flags set to beta=true, where feature_flags contains bet.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""data.retry_count"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta=true""}, {""path"": ""data.retry_count"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""bet""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: audit-logger-config
  namespace: data
data:
  feature_flags: beta=true
  retry_count: '10'",ConfigMap,8
29,The web-app-cron CronJob operates in the production namespace. It is configured with executing on the */5 * * * * cron schedule. It is configured with built from centos:1.2. It has requesting 2 CPU.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/5 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""centos:1.2""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: web-app-cron
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: ssl-terminator
spec:
  schedule: '*/5 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: runner
            image: centos:1.2
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - echo hello
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: '2'
                memory: 1Gi
          restartPolicy: Never",CronJob,6
30,The session-store-config ConfigMap operates in the data namespace. It has carrying label app: worker. It includes cache_ttl configured as 3600. It has the cache_ttl value including 360. It has containing max_connections set to 10.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3600""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""360""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: session-store-config
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: worker
data:
  max_connections: '10'
  cache_ttl: '3600'",ConfigMap,7
31,"Please configure a Service identified as feature-store-svc within staging. Make sure it has operating on TCP, and with service type ClusterIP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}]","apiVersion: v1
