32,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name audit-logger-pod, deployed to production. Specifications include setting SECRET_KEY to false, running prom/prometheus:1.0, and listening on port 15672.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""false""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: audit-logger-pod
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: audit-logger
spec:
  restartPolicy: Always
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: prom/prometheus:1.0
    ports:
    - containerPort: 15672
    env:
    - name: SECRET_KEY
      value: 'false'
    imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent",Pod,6
33,"Set up a Service called file-uploader-svc in the development namespace. It should have exposing port 8080, additionally of type ClusterIP, and also with target port set to 9000, routing to pods where app is rate-limiter.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9000""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
