34,The report-gen-pod Pod operates in the monitoring namespace. It has ruby:16 as its container image. It includes a restart policy of Always. It features allocated 750m CPU.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""750m""}]","apiVersion: v1
