35,The auth-service Deployment operates in the production namespace. It has requesting 500m CPU. It requires scaled to 10 instances. It includes whose container is called server. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. It is configured with a Recreate rollout strategy. It includes redis:17 as its container image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""redis:17""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""500m""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: auth-service
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: auth-service
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: auth-service
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: auth-service
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: redis:17
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 64Mi",Deployment,8
36,"Spin up a Service called analytics-engine-svc in the default namespace. It should have forwarding to target port 9092, labeled team=ml, operating as a NodePort service, with TCP as the transport protocol.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""analytics-engine-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9092""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
