  serviceAccountName: app-sa",Pod,5
40,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name proxy-server, deployed to data. Specifications include running in a container named worker, with 1 replicas, with container port 8200, employing RollingUpdate for deployments, pulling ruby:3.1.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""proxy-server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:3.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8200""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: proxy-server
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: proxy-server
    release: stable
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: proxy-server
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: proxy-server
        release: stable
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: ruby:3.1
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8200
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 128Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 4Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Never
        env:
        - name: MAX_RETRIES
          value: 'false'",Deployment,8
41,"Set up a Deployment called config-server in the default namespace. It should have the container labeled app, with a replica count of 8, and pulling bitnami/kafka:4.0.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""config-server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: config-server
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: config-server
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: config-server
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: config-server
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: bitnami/kafka:4.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5432
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 4Gi",Deployment,6
42,Configure a Service called batch-processor-svc in the infra namespace. It should have of type LoadBalancer.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}]","apiVersion: v1
