43,"Please configure a Deployment identified as email-sender within monitoring. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. Make sure it has Recreate as the strategy type, with golang:16 as the base image, needing 1000m of CPU, naming the container app, and maintaining 1 pods.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1000m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: email-sender
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: email-sender
    env: staging
    team: frontend
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: email-sender
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: email-sender
        env: staging
        team: frontend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: golang:16
        ports:
        - containerPort: 6379
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 1000m
            memory: 64Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 128Mi
        env:
        - name: REDIS_URL
          value: 'false'",Deployment,8
44,"We need a Service named event-bus-svc in logging. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. The configuration requires tagged as env=development, and also exposed externally on port 31524, with port 5000 open, set up as NodePort, matching pods carrying app=log-aggregator.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.nodePort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""31524""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: event-bus-svc
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: event-bus
    env: development
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: log-aggregator
  ports:
  - port: 5000
    targetPort: 8500
    protocol: UDP
    nodePort: 31524",Service,8
45,The model-trainer Deployment operates in the data namespace. It includes having 3 replicated pods. It includes running in a container named model-trainer. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. It is configured with container port 443. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. It has elasticsearch:16 as the base image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""elasticsearch:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: model-trainer
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: model-trainer
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: model-trainer
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: model-trainer
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: model-trainer
        image: elasticsearch:16
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,7
46,The cdn-origin Deployment operates in the development namespace. It requires built from nginx:14. It requires deployed via RollingUpdate. It has its container called main. It has scaled to 1 instances.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nginx:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
