50,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name ml-inference, deployed to production. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. Specifications include with its container called server, built from ruby:3.9, and running 10 copies.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:3.9""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: ml-inference
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: ml-inference
    tier: backend
    team: frontend
    version: v3.0
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: ml-inference
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: ml-inference
        tier: backend
        team: frontend
        version: v3.0
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: ruby:3.9
        ports:
        - containerPort: 1883
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 1000m
            memory: 4Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: WORKERS
          value: 'true'",Deployment,6
51,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name feature-store-svc, deployed to platform. Specifications include listening on port 8200, and also with UDP as the transport protocol, proxying to port 443 on the backend, and also forwarding traffic to pods with app=api-server, and also operating as a ClusterIP service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8200""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server""}]","apiVersion: v1
