53,"Provision a Pod called health-checker-pod in the platform namespace. It should have bearing the app label health-checker, and also running in a container named server, pulling images with policy Never, and also based on the node:3.9 image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""node:3.9""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker""}]","apiVersion: v1
