55,The search-engine-pod Pod operates in the default namespace. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. It is configured with pulling minio/minio:16. It requires naming the container main. It features setting CACHE_TTL to debug. It requires restart mode set to Never. It has needing 64Mi memory.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""minio/minio:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debug""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""64Mi""}]","apiVersion: v1
