57,The user-service-config ConfigMap operates in the logging namespace. It requires tagged as team=infra. It includes including a app_name data key. It requires a feature_flags entry present. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. It is configured with mapping feature_flags to beta=true. It is configured with where app_name contains ima.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""ima""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta=true""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
