59,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name worker-pod, deployed to infra. Specifications include the container identified as runner, allocated 500m CPU, and also based on the prom/prometheus:5.0 image, bearing the app label worker, using Never image pull policy.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:5.0""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""runner""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""500m""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
