60,"Spin up a CronJob called report-gen-cron in the ml namespace. It should have restarting on OnFailure, additionally preserving the last 5 successful runs, with its container called worker, based on the consul:14 image, executing on the 0 * * * * cron schedule.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""consul:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
