64,"Deploy a Deployment called report-gen in the default namespace. It should have a replica count of 6, and also naming the container app, built from consul:14, and exposing container port 4222.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""consul:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: report-gen
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: report-gen
    env: testing
    tier: backend
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: report-gen
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: report-gen
        env: testing
        tier: backend
    spec:
