        - name: NODE_ENV
          value: info",Deployment,7
65,The log-aggregator-svc Service operates in the staging namespace. It features service type NodePort. It features targeting pods with app=web-app. It features communicating over TCP.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}]","apiVersion: v1
