66,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name file-uploader-cron, deployed to infra. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. Specifications include retaining 3 failed job records, set to fire at 0 3 * * 1-5, and using restart policy OnFailure.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 3 * * 1-5""}, {""path"": ""spec.failedJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: file-uploader-cron
  namespace: infra
spec:
  schedule: 0 3 * * 1-5
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: minio/minio:11
            command:
            - python
            - run_job.py
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 500m
                memory: 4Gi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 3",CronJob,6
