72,"Set up a CronJob called load-balancer-cron in the default namespace. It should have triggered by cron expression */10 * * * *, and preserving the last 2 failed runs.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""load-balancer-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/10 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.failedJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
