74,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name log-aggregator, deployed to development. Specifications include with RollingUpdate as the strategy type, using busybox:16 as its container image, maintaining 3 pods, running in a container named app.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: log-aggregator
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: log-aggregator
    team: infra
    version: v2.0
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: log-aggregator
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: log-aggregator
        team: infra
