76,The stream-consumer-config ConfigMap operates in the staging namespace. It has app_name containing the text pay. It requires where log_level contains war. It features which includes a cache_ttl key. It is configured with where the allowed_origins field is *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""pay""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.log_level"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""war""}]","apiVersion: v1
