90,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name batch-processor, deployed to default. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. Specifications include the container identified as batch-processor, additionally using centos:8 as its container image, running 8 copies, and accepting connections on container port 9092.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""centos:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9092""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: batch-processor
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: batch-processor
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: batch-processor
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
