92,The scheduler-ingress Ingress operates in the production namespace. It has serving on port 443. It is configured with routing requests to cdn.example.com. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. It includes handling the /api endpoint. It has forwarding requests to the user-service-svc service. It requires path matching set to Prefix.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/api""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
