98,"Spin up a CronJob called cache-proxy-cron in the staging namespace. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. It should have running on schedule 0 * * * *, naming the container job.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""job""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy-cron
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    env: staging
spec:
  schedule: 0 * * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: job
            image: rabbitmq:1.2
            command:
            - curl
            - -s
            - http://api/health
          restartPolicy: Never
  suspend: false
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 2",CronJob,5
99,Spin up a Pod called webhook-relay-pod in the staging namespace. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. It should have based on the httpd:14 image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""httpd:14""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: webhook-relay-pod
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: webhook-relay
    team: ml
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: httpd:14
    ports:
    - containerPort: 4222
    env:
    - name: WORKERS
      value: 'false'
    imagePullPolicy: Never
  serviceAccountName: monitoring-sa",Pod,4
100,"We need a Service named circuit-breaker-svc in infra. The team responsible for this resource can be reached via the platform-ops Slack channel. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. The configuration requires as a ClusterIP service, and also forwarding to target port 5432.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""circuit-breaker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5432""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: circuit-breaker-svc
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: circuit-breaker
    tier: frontend
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: dns-resolver
  ports:
  - port: 8200
    targetPort: 5432
    protocol: UDP",Service,5
101,"Deploy a CronJob called metrics-collector-cron in the default namespace. It should have a restart policy of Never, running on schedule 0 0 1 * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 1 * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: metrics-collector-cron
  namespace: default
  labels:
    team: platform
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 1 * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: runner
            image: mongo:3.9
          restartPolicy: Never
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 2",CronJob,5
102,"Spin up a Service called backend-svc in the logging namespace. It should have as a NodePort service, and with nodePort 31959.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.nodePort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""31959""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: backend-svc
  namespace: logging
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: dns-resolver
  ports:
  - port: 443
    targetPort: 3306
    protocol: TCP
    nodePort: 31959",Service,5
103,"Please configure a Deployment identified as session-store within monitoring. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. Make sure it has traefik:latest as the base image, and also running in a container named session-store, and also with 10 replicas.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""traefik:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: session-store
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: session-store
    release: blue
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: session-store
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: session-store
        release: blue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: session-store
        image: traefik:latest
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 1000m
            memory: 256Mi
          limits:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 2Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Never
        env:
        - name: APP_NAME
          value: production",Deployment,6
104,The scheduler-pod Pod operates in the staging namespace. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. It includes golang:1.1 as the base image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:1.1""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: scheduler-pod
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: scheduler
    team: platform
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: golang:1.1
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: '1'
        memory: 2Gi
    env:
    - name: API_KEY
      value: 'false'
    imagePullPolicy: Always",Pod,4
105,"Set up a Deployment called cache-proxy in the ml namespace. It should have having 3 replicated pods, and also based on the debian:14 image, the container identified as worker.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debian:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: cache-proxy
    env: staging
    tier: cache
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cache-proxy
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cache-proxy
        env: staging
        tier: cache
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: debian:14
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9092
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: CACHE_TTL
          value: '60'",Deployment,6
106,"Please configure a ConfigMap identified as cdn-origin-config within development. Make sure it has annotated with env=testing, where the timeout_seconds field is 10, with retry_count configured as 3.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""testing""}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""data.retry_count"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
