108,"Spin up a Pod called cron-runner-pod in the monitoring namespace. It should have running nginx:16, running under service account admin.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nginx:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.serviceAccountName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""admin""}]","apiVersion: v1
