  namespace: monitoring
data:
  feature_flags: beta=true
  workers: '1'
  allowed_origins: https://app.example.com
  app_name: report-gen
  timeout_seconds: '120'
  max_connections: '100'",ConfigMap,6
110,The config-server-pod Pod operates in the default namespace. It features labeled team=frontend. It has the container labeled runner. It includes carrying the app=config-server label. It includes traefik:5.0 as the base image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""config-server-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""traefik:5.0""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""runner""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""config-server""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
