111,We need a CronJob named order-service-cron in data. The configuration requires running on schedule 0 * * * *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 * * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
