                cpu: 750m
                memory: 128Mi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,4
112,"Deploy a ConfigMap called image-processor-config in the ml namespace. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. It should have storing app_name with value log-aggregator, where redis_host contains red, having app_name match the substring log, including a timeout_seconds data key.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.redis_host"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""red""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""log""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: image-processor-config
  namespace: ml
data:
  timeout_seconds: '10'
  app_env: production
  max_connections: '100'
  app_name: log-aggregator
  app_port: '8080'
  redis_host: redis://redis-master:6379",ConfigMap,7
113,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name image-processor-config, deployed to infra. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. Specifications include where the database_url entry includes mys, containing max_connections set to 50, and also where the database_url field is mysql://db:3306/app.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50""}, {""path"": ""data.database_url"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql://db:3306/app""}, {""path"": ""data.database_url"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""mys""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: image-processor-config
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: report-gen
data:
  max_connections: '50'
  database_url: mysql://db:3306/app
  redis_host: redis://redis:6379
  retry_count: '3'
  allowed_origins: '*'
  debug_mode: 'false'",ConfigMap,6
114,"Please configure a CronJob identified as ml-inference-cron within infra. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. Make sure it has successfulJobsHistoryLimit set to 5, retaining 2 failed job records, with the cron schedule 0 0 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.failedJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: ml-inference-cron
  namespace: infra
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: job
            image: ruby:slim
          restartPolicy: Never
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 2",CronJob,6
115,"Spin up a CronJob called log-aggregator-cron in the development namespace. It should have retaining 5 successful job records, restart mode set to OnFailure, while also scheduled at 0 */2 * * *, and with its container called cron.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */2 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: log-aggregator-cron
  namespace: development
spec:
  schedule: 0 */2 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
