        - containerPort: 11211",Deployment,6
117,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name frontend-cron, deployed to monitoring. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. Specifications include triggered by cron expression 0 6 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 6 * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
