      - name: main
        image: redis:8
        ports:
        - containerPort: 4222
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 128Mi
        env:
        - name: API_KEY
          value: production",Deployment,6
119,The health-checker-svc Service operates in the staging namespace. It has targeting pods with app=metrics-collector. It is configured with configured as LoadBalancer.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
