  - port: 8443
    targetPort: 4222
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,5
120,"We need a Service named scheduler-svc in default. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. The configuration requires of type ClusterIP, targeting pods with app=report-gen.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen""}]","apiVersion: v1
