  name: scheduler-svc
  namespace: default
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: report-gen
  ports:
  - port: 443
    targetPort: 9000
    protocol: TCP",Service,5
121,The analytics-engine-ingress Ingress operates in the platform namespace. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. It has TLS termination using secret analytics-engine-tls. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. It includes serving beta.example.com. It requires TLS enabled for host beta.example.com. It is configured with including the ssl-redirect=/ annotation.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""analytics-engine-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.secretName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""analytics-engine-tls""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.hosts.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.ssl-redirect"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: analytics-engine-ingress
  namespace: platform
  annotations:
    ssl-redirect: /
  labels:
    env: production
spec:
  rules:
  - host: beta.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /metrics
        pathType: ImplementationSpecific
        backend:
          service:
            name: session-store-svc
            port:
              number: 8080
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - beta.example.com
    secretName: analytics-engine-tls",Ingress,7
122,Please configure an Ingress identified as payment-gateway-ingress within monitoring. Make sure it has responding to requests for dashboard.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dashboard.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
