125,"Set up a Deployment called notification-svc in the production namespace. It should have exposing container port 11211, and also having 10 replicated pods, while also based on the mysql:alpine image, with the container labeled worker.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""11211""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: notification-svc
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: notification-svc
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: notification-svc
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: notification-svc
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: mysql:alpine
