        - containerPort: 11211
        imagePullPolicy: Never
        env:
        - name: TIMEOUT
          value: 'false'",Deployment,7
126,"Spin up a Deployment called event-bus in the default namespace. It should have kibana:1.1 as its container image, having 5 replicated pods, while also whose container is called server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""kibana:1.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: event-bus
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: event-bus
    tier: cache
