127,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name frontend-ingress, deployed to production. Specifications include directing traffic for the host status.example.com, and also using ingress class traefik, with a Exact pathType, and with port 3000 open.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""status.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Exact""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3000""}, {""path"": ""spec.ingressClassName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""traefik""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: frontend-ingress
  namespace: production
  annotations:
    rewrite-target: 'true'
  labels:
    env: production
spec:
  rules:
  - host: status.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v1
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: circuit-breaker-svc
            port:
              number: 3000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - status.example.com
    secretName: frontend-tls
  ingressClassName: traefik",Ingress,7
128,"Configure a Deployment called catalog-api in the data namespace. It should have the container labeled main, having 8 replicated pods, needing 750m of CPU, running memcached:16.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""750m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: catalog-api
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: catalog-api
    version: v1.0
    team: infra
    env: staging
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: catalog-api
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: catalog-api
        version: v1.0
        team: infra
        env: staging
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: memcached:16
        ports:
        - containerPort: 27017
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 1Gi",Deployment,7
129,"We need a Deployment named cache-proxy in production. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. The configuration requires environment variable LOG_LEVEL=false, with its container called worker, additionally running ubuntu:alpine, and running 6 copies.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ubuntu:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""false""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: cache-proxy
    team: data
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cache-proxy
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cache-proxy
        team: data
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: ubuntu:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 1883
        env:
        - name: LOG_LEVEL
          value: 'false'",Deployment,7
130,Please configure a Pod identified as scheduler-pod within staging. Make sure it has centos:1.1 as the base image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""centos:1.1""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
