    imagePullPolicy: Never",Pod,4
131,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name worker-pod, deployed to ml. Specifications include restarting on Never, exposing the REDIS_URL environment variable, pulling prom/prometheus:14.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""REDIS_URL""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
