132,"Create a Deployment called cron-runner in the data namespace. It should have based on the debian:8 image, with its container called server, and scaled to 5 instances.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debian:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cron-runner
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: cron-runner
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cron-runner
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cron-runner
    spec:
