133,"Please configure a ConfigMap identified as payment-gateway-config within data. Make sure it has debug_mode configured as false, with redis_host configured as redis://redis:6379, additionally having the app_port field, where cache_ttl contains 360, and having cache_ttl=3600 in its data.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3600""}, {""path"": ""data.debug_mode"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""false""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""360""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.redis_host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""redis://redis:6379""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: payment-gateway-config
  namespace: data
data:
  app_port: '5000'
  api_key_prefix: sk-
  cache_ttl: '3600'
  debug_mode: 'false'
  redis_host: redis://redis:6379",ConfigMap,8
134,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name worker-config, deployed to default. Specifications include which includes a log_level key.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""data.log_level"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: worker-config
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: email-sender
data:
  app_port: '8080'
  log_level: warn
  allowed_origins: '*'
  rate_limit: '1000'
  max_connections: '500'
  cache_ttl: '600'",ConfigMap,4
135,The rate-limiter-svc Service operates in the default namespace. It features operating as a NodePort service.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}]","apiVersion: v1
