    nodePort: 30805",Service,4
136,We need a ConfigMap named stream-consumer-config in platform.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
