  retry_count: '3'
  app_name: user-service
  redis_host: redis://redis-master:6379
  max_connections: '500'
  feature_flags: enable_v2=true
  api_key_prefix: sk-",ConfigMap,3
137,The frontend-config ConfigMap operates in the platform namespace. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. It features the env label set to production.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: frontend-config
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    env: production
data:
  feature_flags: enable_v2=true
  app_name: gateway
  cache_ttl: '60'
  workers: '1'",ConfigMap,4
138,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name api-server-cron, deployed to ml. Specifications include executing a command that begins with /bin/sh, retaining 5 successful job records, and also running on schedule */10 * * * *, with a restart policy of OnFailure, based on the busybox:16 image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/10 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.command.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/bin/sh""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: api-server-cron
  namespace: ml
spec:
  schedule: '*/10 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: job
            image: busybox:16
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - date; echo done
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 2",CronJob,8
139,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name inventory-svc-svc, deployed to monitoring. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. Specifications include operating as a ClusterIP service, and with sticky sessions via ClientIP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: inventory-svc-svc
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: session-store
  ports:
  - port: 15672
    targetPort: 3306
    protocol: TCP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,5
140,"We need a Deployment named payment-gateway in monitoring. The configuration requires whose container is called payment-gateway, while also declaring the REDIS_URL env var, using prom/prometheus:stable as its container image, and having 8 replicated pods.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:stable""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""REDIS_URL""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: payment-gateway
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: payment-gateway
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: payment-gateway
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: payment-gateway
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: payment-gateway
        image: prom/prometheus:stable
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5432
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 2Gi
        env:
        - name: REDIS_URL
          value: 'false'",Deployment,7
141,The webhook-relay-svc Service operates in the ml namespace. It features matching pods carrying app=api-server. It features as a LoadBalancer service. It is configured with targeting port 80.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: webhook-relay-svc
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: webhook-relay
    team: devops
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: api-server
  ports:
  - port: 9000
    targetPort: 80
    protocol: UDP",Service,6
142,"Configure an Ingress called scheduler-ingress in the development namespace. It should have routed through the nginx ingress class, while also handling the /api/v1 endpoint, annotated with env=production, and also handling traffic for status.example.com, while also forwarding requests to the cache-proxy-svc service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""status.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/api/v1""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.ingressClassName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nginx""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-svc""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: scheduler-ingress
  namespace: development
  annotations:
    rewrite-target: /
  labels:
    env: production
spec:
  rules:
  - host: status.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v1
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: cache-proxy-svc
            port:
              number: 80
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - status.example.com
    secretName: scheduler-tls
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,8
143,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name service-mesh-pod, deployed to infra. Specifications include listening on port 11211, pulling python:4.0, bearing the label team=infra.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""service-mesh-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:4.0""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""11211""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: service-mesh-pod
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: service-mesh
    team: infra
spec:
  restartPolicy: Never
  containers:
  - name: app
