      value: 'false'
    imagePullPolicy: Never",Pod,6
144,"Please configure a Service identified as data-pipeline-svc within monitoring. Make sure it has via TCP, targeting port 443, routing to pods where app is frontend, and set up as ClusterIP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: data-pipeline-svc
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: frontend
  ports:
  - port: 6379
    targetPort: 443
