145,Please configure a CronJob identified as report-gen-cron within development. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. Make sure it has set to fire at 0 0 * * 0.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 * * 0""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: report-gen-cron
  namespace: development
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 * * 0
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: bitnami/kafka:21
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - cleanup.sh
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: '1'
                memory: 1Gi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure",CronJob,4
146,"Configure a Deployment called gateway in the ml namespace. It should have exposing container port 8080, and also using consul:8 as its container image, with the container labeled app, and scaled to 5 instances.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""consul:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: gateway
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: gateway
    env: testing
    tier: queue
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: gateway
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: gateway
        env: testing
        tier: queue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: consul:8
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 1Gi",Deployment,7
147,The stream-consumer-config ConfigMap operates in the data namespace. It requires having the app_port field. It features where the allowed_origins entry includes htt.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""htt""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: stream-consumer-config
  namespace: data
data:
  app_port: '3000'
  app_env: development
  api_key_prefix: pk-
  redis_host: redis://redis-master:6379
