148,The report-gen Deployment operates in the production namespace. It features the container labeled app. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. It is configured with running nats:20. It includes a replica count of 3. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. It requires bearing the label team=devops.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:20""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""devops""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: report-gen
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: report-gen
    team: devops
    env: testing
    version: v3
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: report-gen
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: report-gen
        team: devops
        env: testing
        version: v3
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: nats:20
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9090
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 128Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 4Gi",Deployment,7
149,The payment-gateway-ingress Ingress operates in the production namespace. It requires ingress class haproxy. It is configured with exposing port 80. It has handling traffic for shop.example.com. It includes handling the /admin endpoint.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""shop.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/admin""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}, {""path"": ""spec.ingressClassName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""haproxy""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: payment-gateway-ingress
  namespace: production
  annotations:
    rewrite-target: 'true'
spec:
  rules:
  - host: shop.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /admin
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: ssl-terminator-svc
            port:
              number: 80
  ingressClassName: haproxy",Ingress,7
150,"Spin up an Ingress called image-processor-ingress in the monitoring namespace. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. It should have matching /health, with port 8080 open, with a ImplementationSpecific pathType, and bound to host ws.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ws.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/health""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ImplementationSpecific""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: image-processor-ingress
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  rules:
  - host: ws.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /health
        pathType: ImplementationSpecific
        backend:
          service:
            name: ssl-terminator-svc
            port:
              number: 8080
  ingressClassName: istio",Ingress,7
151,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name proxy-server-svc, deployed to monitoring. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Specifications include with session affinity set to ClientIP, and also routing to pods where app is circuit-breaker, with target port set to 8080, additionally as a NodePort service, serving on port 27017.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""proxy-server-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""27017""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""circuit-breaker""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: proxy-server-svc
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: circuit-breaker
  ports:
  - port: 27017
    targetPort: 8080
    protocol: TCP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,8
152,"We need a Deployment named data-pipeline in staging. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. The configuration requires based on the kibana:slim image, while also running in a container named worker, pulling images with policy Always, and having 1 replicated pods.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""kibana:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: data-pipeline
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: data-pipeline
    release: stable
    team: backend
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: data-pipeline
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: data-pipeline
        release: stable
        team: backend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: kibana:slim
        ports:
        - containerPort: 11211
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 256Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 64Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always",Deployment,7
153,"We need a CronJob named inventory-svc-cron in development. The configuration requires running bitnami/kafka:5.0, restarting on OnFailure, and also scheduled at 0 */6 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */6 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:5.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: inventory-svc-cron
  namespace: development
spec:
  schedule: 0 */6 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: bitnami/kafka:5.0
            command:
            - curl
            - -s
            - http://api/health
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 3",CronJob,6
154,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name dns-resolver-svc, deployed to monitoring. Specifications include with UDP as the transport protocol, listening on port 9090, and configured as LoadBalancer.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: dns-resolver-svc
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: report-gen
  ports:
  - port: 9090
    targetPort: 9092
    protocol: UDP",Service,6
155,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name search-engine-config, deployed to logging. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Specifications include with a max_connections entry present, with a timeout_seconds entry present, and where the timeout_seconds field is 60.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""60""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
