157,The metrics-collector-cron CronJob operates in the platform namespace. It has scheduled at 30 2 * * *. It is configured with a restart policy of OnFailure. It is configured with the container labeled cron. It has running vault:1.1. It requires not currently suspended.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""30 2 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:1.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron""}, {""path"": ""spec.suspend"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""False""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: metrics-collector-cron
  namespace: platform
spec:
  schedule: 30 2 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: cron
            image: vault:1.1
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  concurrencyPolicy: Allow
  suspend: false",CronJob,8
158,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name circuit-breaker-svc, deployed to default. Specifications include listening on port 8200, and also with target port set to 9000, and as a ClusterIP service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""circuit-breaker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9000""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8200""}]","apiVersion: v1
