    - containerPort: 8500
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: 250m
        memory: 1Gi",Pod,8
160,"We need a Deployment named order-service in data. The configuration requires running in a container named app, maintaining 4 pods, including CACHE_TTL in its environment, pulling envoyproxy/envoy:alpine.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""envoyproxy/envoy:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CACHE_TTL""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: order-service
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: order-service
    team: backend
    release: green
    tier: queue
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: order-service
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: order-service
        team: backend
        release: green
        tier: queue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: envoyproxy/envoy:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9090
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 4Gi
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
        env:
        - name: CACHE_TTL
          value: 'false'",Deployment,7
161,"We need a Deployment named worker in data. The configuration requires naming the container worker, using mysql:16 as its container image, and with 3 replicas.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
