            cpu: 200m
            memory: 128Mi",Deployment,8
171,The rate-limiter-svc Service operates in the platform namespace. It features of type NodePort. It features bearing the label team=frontend.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: rate-limiter-svc
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: rate-limiter
    team: frontend
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: inventory-svc
  ports:
  - port: 11211
    targetPort: 3306
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,5
172,"Please configure a Deployment identified as pdf-generator within logging. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. Make sure it has based on the envoyproxy/envoy:1.0 image, configuring the APP_NAME variable, with its container called worker, scaled to 10 instances.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""envoyproxy/envoy:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""APP_NAME""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: pdf-generator
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: pdf-generator
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: pdf-generator
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: envoyproxy/envoy:1.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5432
        env:
        - name: APP_NAME
          value: 'true'",Deployment,7
173,"We need an Ingress named cdn-origin-ingress in monitoring. The configuration requires handling the /api/v1 endpoint, forwarding requests to the data-pipeline-svc service, exposing port 8080, and routing requests to ws.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ws.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/api/v1""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: cdn-origin-ingress
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  rules:
  - host: ws.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v1
        pathType: ImplementationSpecific
        backend:
          service:
            name: data-pipeline-svc
            port:
              number: 8080",Ingress,7
174,The scheduler-config ConfigMap operates in the ml namespace.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}]","apiVersion: v1
