  app_port: '5000'
  api_key_prefix: api-",ConfigMap,3
175,The queue-worker Deployment operates in the infra namespace. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. It is configured with pulling redis:alpine. It features naming the container worker. It has running 2 copies.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""queue-worker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""redis:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: queue-worker
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: queue-worker
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: queue-worker
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: queue-worker
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: redis:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 6379
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 256Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Never
        env:
        - name: JWT_SECRET
          value: '3'",Deployment,6
176,We need a Service named pdf-generator-svc in infra. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. The configuration requires configured as LoadBalancer.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
