  name: pdf-generator-svc
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
    env: staging
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: circuit-breaker
  ports:
  - port: 1883
    targetPort: 6379
    protocol: TCP",Service,4
177,"Configure a Deployment called event-bus in the data namespace. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. It should have running kibana:1.2, additionally having 1 replicated pods, where JWT_SECRET equals info, and whose container is called server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""kibana:1.2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""info""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: event-bus
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: event-bus
    release: blue
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: event-bus
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: event-bus
        release: blue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: kibana:1.2
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 64Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: JWT_SECRET
          value: info",Deployment,7
178,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name pdf-generator, deployed to ml. Specifications include based on the redis:latest image, maintaining 4 pods, and the container identified as main.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""redis:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
