        image: redis:latest
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 256Mi",Deployment,6
179,"We need a Deployment named cache-proxy in development. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. The configuration requires 5 replicas, and also with its container called main, based on the traefik:17 image, and serving on container port 3000.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""traefik:17""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3000""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: cache-proxy
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cache-proxy
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cache-proxy
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: traefik:17
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 64Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 128Mi",Deployment,7
180,"Please configure a Service identified as image-processor-svc within development. Make sure it has routing to backend port 80, with sticky sessions via ClientIP, with service type ClusterIP, via UDP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: image-processor-svc
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: image-processor
    team: devops
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: webhook-relay
  ports:
  - port: 4222
    targetPort: 80
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,7
181,"Create a Deployment called rate-limiter in the production namespace. It should have its container called main, while also based on the memcached:8 image, additionally with 2 replicas.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
