209,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name config-server, deployed to monitoring. Specifications include having 6 replicated pods, based on the prom/prometheus:21 image, whose container is called server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""config-server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:21""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: config-server
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: config-server
    team: data
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: config-server
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: config-server
        team: data
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: prom/prometheus:21
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: API_KEY
          value: info",Deployment,6
210,We need a CronJob named config-server-cron in development. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. The configuration requires the cron schedule */5 * * * *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""config-server-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/5 * * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: config-server-cron
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
spec:
  schedule: '*/5 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: minio/minio:alpine
          restartPolicy: Never
  concurrencyPolicy: Allow
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 3",CronJob,4
211,"Configure a Pod called cache-proxy-pod in the development namespace. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. It should have bearing the app label cache-proxy, while also naming the container main, serving on port 8080, with a restart policy of Never, running busybox:1.1.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:1.1""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy-pod
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: cache-proxy
spec:
  restartPolicy: Never
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: busybox:1.1
    ports:
    - containerPort: 8080",Pod,8
212,"Provision a Deployment called feature-store in the logging namespace. It should have maintaining 3 pods, bearing the label team=infra, whose container is called server, additionally using prom/prometheus:20 as its container image, and with the env label set to staging.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:20""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: feature-store
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: feature-store
    team: infra
    tier: cache
    env: staging
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: feature-store
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: feature-store
        team: infra
        tier: cache
        env: staging
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: prom/prometheus:20
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5432
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 128Mi",Deployment,8
213,"Provision a ConfigMap called config-server-config in the platform namespace. It should have containing app_port set to 5000, and also with max_connections configured as 50, with the app_port value including 500, and with a log_level entry present.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""config-server-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""data.log_level"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""500""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}]","apiVersion: v1
