data:
  max_connections: '50'
  log_level: warn
  app_port: '5000'",ConfigMap,7
214,The image-processor-ingress Ingress operates in the data namespace. It includes serving blog.example.com. It is configured with ingress class haproxy. It features matching /admin. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. It features having the annotation rewrite-target configured to Ingress.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""blog.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.rewrite-target"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress for image-processor-ingress""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/admin""}, {""path"": ""spec.ingressClassName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""haproxy""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: image-processor-ingress
  namespace: data
  annotations:
    rewrite-target: Ingress for image-processor-ingress
  labels:
    env: production
spec:
  rules:
  - host: blog.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /admin
        pathType: ImplementationSpecific
        backend:
          service:
            name: cron-runner-svc
            port:
              number: 8080
  ingressClassName: haproxy",Ingress,7
215,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name webhook-relay, deployed to development. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Specifications include maintaining 1 pods, deployed via RollingUpdate, the container identified as main, environment variable PORT=info, while also built from grafana/grafana:3.9.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:3.9""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""info""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: webhook-relay
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: webhook-relay
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: webhook-relay
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: webhook-relay
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: grafana/grafana:3.9
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        env:
        - name: PORT
          value: info",Deployment,8
216,Create a ConfigMap called health-checker-config in the default namespace.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: health-checker-config
  namespace: default
  labels:
    team: infra
data:
