220,The session-store-pod Pod operates in the logging namespace. It features OnFailure restart behavior. It has carrying the app=session-store label. It is configured with the container labeled server. It features running elasticsearch:5.0.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""elasticsearch:5.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}]","apiVersion: v1
