221,"Create a CronJob called ml-inference-cron in the staging namespace. It should have running on schedule */10 * * * *, and with a restart policy of Never.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/10 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: ml-inference-cron
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: ml-inference
spec:
  schedule: '*/10 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: job
            image: busybox:1.0
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - cleanup.sh
          restartPolicy: Never
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,5
222,"Please configure a Pod identified as health-checker-pod within infra. Make sure it has restart mode set to Never, reserving 50m CPU resources, while also with its container called app, while also requesting 128Mi of memory, and based on the ruby:1.0 image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50m""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""128Mi""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
