        cpu: 50m
        memory: 128Mi",Pod,8
223,"We need a CronJob named worker-cron in platform. The configuration requires the container labeled worker, with the cron schedule */10 * * * *, and restarting on Never.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/10 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: worker-cron
  namespace: platform
spec:
  schedule: '*/10 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: postgres:17
          restartPolicy: Never
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5",CronJob,6
224,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name health-checker-svc, deployed to development. Specifications include targeting pods with app=backend, as a LoadBalancer service, additionally using TCP protocol.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: health-checker-svc
  namespace: development
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: backend
  ports:
  - port: 5432
    targetPort: 443
    protocol: TCP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,6
225,The gateway-pod Pod operates in the infra namespace. It is configured with built from openjdk:3.0. It has the app label set to gateway.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""openjdk:3.0""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
