  name: gateway-pod
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: gateway
    tier: backend
spec:
  restartPolicy: Never
  containers:
  - name: worker
    image: openjdk:3.0
    ports:
    - containerPort: 4222
    imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
  serviceAccountName: app-sa",Pod,5
226,"Deploy a Deployment called audit-logger in the ml namespace. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. It should have naming the container server, and also pulling golang:1.1, and scaled to 3 instances.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:1.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: audit-logger
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: audit-logger
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: audit-logger
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: audit-logger
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: golang:1.1
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9092
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent",Deployment,6
227,The dns-resolver-cron CronJob operates in the logging namespace. It has whose container is called runner. It is configured with bearing the label team=platform. It features scheduled at */5 * * * *. It features reserving 1000m CPU resources. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. It requires envoyproxy/envoy:stable as its container image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/5 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""runner""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1000m""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""envoyproxy/envoy:stable""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: dns-resolver-cron
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    team: platform
spec:
  schedule: '*/5 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: runner
            image: envoyproxy/envoy:stable
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 1000m
                memory: 2Gi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  concurrencyPolicy: Replace",CronJob,8
228,"We need a Deployment named worker in ml. The configuration requires pulling bitnami/kafka:3.0, with imagePullPolicy set to Never, scaled to 5 instances, annotated with env=production, and whose container is called app.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: worker
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: worker
    env: production
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: worker
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: worker
        env: production
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: bitnami/kafka:3.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 256Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,8
229,"Deploy a Service called scheduler-svc in the platform namespace. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. It should have of type NodePort, and with UDP as the transport protocol.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: scheduler-svc
  namespace: platform
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: file-uploader
  ports:
  - port: 8443
    targetPort: 4222
    protocol: UDP",Service,5
230,The report-gen Deployment operates in the data namespace. It has pulling python:1.0. It is configured with 4 replicas. It requires the container identified as main.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
