231,"We need a Deployment named queue-worker in development. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. The configuration requires the container labeled app, while also using vault:16 as its container image, and maintaining 2 pods.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""queue-worker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: queue-worker
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: queue-worker
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: queue-worker
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: queue-worker
    spec:
