        ports:
        - containerPort: 9000
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent",Deployment,6
232,"Configure a Pod called metrics-collector-pod in the development namespace. The team responsible for this resource can be reached via the platform-ops Slack channel. It should have centos:1.0 as the base image, using service account app-sa, with its container called app, and including APP_NAME in its environment.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""centos:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""APP_NAME""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.serviceAccountName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app-sa""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: metrics-collector-pod
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: metrics-collector
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: app
    image: centos:1.0
    env:
    - name: APP_NAME
      value: debug
    imagePullPolicy: Never
  serviceAccountName: app-sa",Pod,7
233,"Create a Deployment called webhook-relay in the monitoring namespace. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. It should have maintaining 4 pods, with the container labeled app, and built from mongo:1.2.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongo:1.2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: webhook-relay
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: webhook-relay
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: webhook-relay
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: webhook-relay
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: mongo:1.2
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 2Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 64Mi",Deployment,6
234,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name scheduler-ingress, deployed to infra. Specifications include responding to requests for ws.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ws.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: scheduler-ingress
  namespace: infra
  annotations:
    proxy-body-size: /
spec:
  rules:
  - host: ws.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: catalog-api-svc
            port:
              number: 5000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - ws.example.com
    secretName: scheduler-tls
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,4
235,Please configure a ConfigMap identified as pdf-generator-config within platform. Make sure it has containing retry_count set to 3.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""data.retry_count"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}]","apiVersion: v1
