  name: pdf-generator-config
  namespace: platform
data:
  app_name: user-service
  workers: '2'
  retry_count: '3'",ConfigMap,4
236,The api-server-config ConfigMap operates in the production namespace. It includes having app_env match the substring pro. It has containing retry_count set to 10. It is configured with where the allowed_origins field is https://app.example.com. It requires containing the app_env entry.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""data.retry_count"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""data.app_env"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""pro""}, {""path"": ""data.app_env"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""https://app.example.com""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: api-server-config
  namespace: production
data:
  app_env: production
  database_url: mongodb://mongo:27017/app
  allowed_origins: https://app.example.com
  retry_count: '10'
  workers: '4'",ConfigMap,7
237,"Deploy a Service called scheduler-svc in the data namespace. It should have the tier label set to monitoring, targeting pods with app=worker, proxying to port 1883 on the backend, with port 8443 open, and operating as a NodePort service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8443""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1883""}]","apiVersion: v1
