    protocol: TCP",Service,8
238,The email-sender-pod Pod operates in the platform namespace. It is configured with running nginx:16.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nginx:16""}]","apiVersion: v1
