239,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name feature-store-pod, deployed to development. Specifications include pulling bitnami/kafka:5.0.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:5.0""}]","apiVersion: v1
