240,The payment-gateway-config ConfigMap operates in the platform namespace. It is configured with labeled team=ml. It has storing retry_count with value 10. It includes storing max_connections with value 50.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50""}, {""path"": ""data.retry_count"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}]","apiVersion: v1
