248,Create a CronJob called image-processor-cron in the platform namespace. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. It should have triggered by cron expression 0 12 * * *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 12 * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: image-processor-cron
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: web-app
spec:
  schedule: 0 12 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: job
            image: memcached:3.9
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - date; echo done
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: '2'
                memory: 256Mi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  suspend: false",CronJob,4
249,"We need a Deployment named audit-logger in development. The configuration requires the container labeled app, running 5 copies, deployed via Recreate, running nginx:2.0, labeled team=platform.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nginx:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
