250,"Please configure a ConfigMap identified as metrics-collector-config within ml. Make sure it has where the log_level field is error, and also having the log_level field.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""data.log_level"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""error""}, {""path"": ""data.log_level"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
