251,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name backend, deployed to development. Specifications include having 4 replicated pods, additionally the container identified as main, running mysql:20.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql:20""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: backend
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: backend
    version: v2.0
    release: blue
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: backend
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: backend
        version: v2.0
        release: blue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: mysql:20
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 64Mi
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent",Deployment,6
252,"We need a Deployment named dns-resolver in data. The configuration requires ubuntu:1.0 as the base image, and also whose container is called dns-resolver, while also having 10 replicated pods, while also labeled env=staging, and also with RollingUpdate as the strategy type.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ubuntu:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
