253,"Please configure a CronJob identified as feature-store-cron within data. Make sure it has suspend set to false, set to fire at 0 * * * *, labeled env=production.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.suspend"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""False""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
