  suspend: false",CronJob,6
254,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name model-trainer, deployed to default. Specifications include pulling nats:alpine, additionally the container identified as app, with a replica count of 10, and needing 512Mi memory.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""512Mi""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: model-trainer
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: model-trainer
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: model-trainer
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: model-trainer
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: nats:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 6379
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 512Mi
        env:
        - name: NODE_ENV
          value: '8080'",Deployment,7
255,The web-app-ingress Ingress operates in the staging namespace. It requires bound to host admin.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""admin.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: web-app-ingress
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    env: production
spec:
  rules:
  - host: admin.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /admin
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: webhook-relay-svc
            port:
              number: 3000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - admin.example.com
    secretName: web-app-tls",Ingress,4
256,The dns-resolver-svc Service operates in the ml namespace. It features of type NodePort. It includes communicating over UDP. It has a node port of 30179. It has port 11211 open.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""11211""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.nodePort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""30179""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: dns-resolver-svc
  namespace: ml
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: backend
  ports:
  - port: 11211
    targetPort: 9092
    protocol: UDP
    nodePort: 30179",Service,7
257,"Provision a Deployment called file-uploader in the default namespace. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. It should have deployed via RollingUpdate, additionally naming the container file-uploader, and also with prom/prometheus:20 as the base image, additionally running 10 copies.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:20""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: file-uploader
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: file-uploader
    env: development
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: file-uploader
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: file-uploader
        env: development
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: file-uploader
        image: prom/prometheus:20
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9090
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 2Gi
        env:
        - name: METRICS_PORT
          value: '8080'",Deployment,7
258,"We need an Ingress named stream-consumer-ingress in default. The configuration requires configured with pathType Prefix, handling traffic for example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: stream-consumer-ingress
  namespace: default
spec:
  rules:
  - host: example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /uploads
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: feature-store-svc
            port:
              number: 443
  ingressClassName: istio",Ingress,5
259,"Create a ConfigMap called ssl-terminator-config in the data namespace. It should have where app_port contains 909, mapping debug_mode to true, and where the app_name entry includes dat.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""dat""}, {""path"": ""data.debug_mode"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""909""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
