        - name: WORKERS
          value: '8080'",Deployment,6
265,The ml-inference Deployment operates in the ml namespace. It has based on the kibana:14 image. It requires the container labeled main. It features allocated 200m CPU. It has scaled to 6 instances.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""kibana:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""200m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: ml-inference
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: ml-inference
    release: green
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: ml-inference
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: ml-inference
        release: green
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: kibana:14
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9092
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 512Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 128Mi",Deployment,7
266,The pdf-generator Deployment operates in the logging namespace. It features the team label set to devops. It has redis:alpine as its container image. It features having 1 replicated pods. It requires running in a container named app.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""redis:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""devops""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: pdf-generator
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
    release: stable
    version: v2.1
    team: devops
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: pdf-generator
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: pdf-generator
        release: stable
        version: v2.1
        team: devops
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: redis:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3306
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 64Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,7
267,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name ml-inference-pod, deployed to logging. Specifications include listening on port 27017, carrying the app=ml-inference label, pulling python:17, additionally with a restart policy of OnFailure.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:17""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""27017""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: ml-inference-pod
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: ml-inference
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
