    - containerPort: 27017",Pod,7
268,The backend-ingress Ingress operates in the staging namespace. It has handling traffic for app.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: backend-ingress
  namespace: staging
spec:
  rules:
  - host: app.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v1
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: order-service-svc
            port:
              number: 443
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - app.example.com
    secretName: backend-tls
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,4
269,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name cache-proxy, deployed to infra. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. Specifications include having 8 replicated pods, and also annotated with tier=cache, running envoyproxy/envoy:17, additionally the container identified as cache-proxy.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""envoyproxy/envoy:17""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: cache-proxy
    tier: cache
    version: v1.0
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cache-proxy
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cache-proxy
        tier: cache
        version: v1.0
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: cache-proxy
        image: envoyproxy/envoy:17
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9200
        env:
        - name: APP_NAME
          value: 'false'",Deployment,7
270,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name auth-service-pod, deployed to ml. Specifications include built from alpine:16, and tagged with app: auth-service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""alpine:16""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}]","apiVersion: v1
