271,We need a ConfigMap named web-app-config in data.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: web-app-config
  namespace: data
data:
  rate_limit: '1000'
  retry_count: '3'
  timeout_seconds: '5'
  log_level: info
  cache_ttl: '300'",ConfigMap,3
272,The web-app Deployment operates in the default namespace. It has allocated 50m CPU. It requires the container identified as server. It features 8 replicas. It requires a memory request of 1Gi. It includes based on the postgres:21 image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""postgres:21""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1Gi""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: web-app
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: web-app
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: web-app
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: web-app
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: postgres:21
        ports:
        - containerPort: 4222
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 1Gi",Deployment,8
273,"We need a Deployment named catalog-api in data. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. The configuration requires naming the container worker, built from minio/minio:3.0, while also having 8 replicated pods.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""minio/minio:3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
