        - containerPort: 4222
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,6
274,"Spin up a Service called notification-svc-svc in the platform namespace. It should have the team label set to frontend, as a ClusterIP service, with target port set to 11211.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""11211""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: notification-svc-svc
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: notification
    team: frontend
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: scheduler
  ports:
  - port: 8200
    targetPort: 11211
    protocol: TCP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,6
275,"Configure a Deployment called log-aggregator in the logging namespace. It should have running in a container named log-aggregator, and also based on the memcached:4.0 image, with 6 replicas, requesting 64Mi of memory, and environment variable JWT_SECRET=3.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""64Mi""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: log-aggregator
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: log-aggregator
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: log-aggregator
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: log-aggregator
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: log-aggregator
        image: memcached:4.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9092
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 64Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 1000m
            memory: 512Mi
        env:
        - name: JWT_SECRET
          value: '3'",Deployment,8
276,"Please configure a Deployment identified as event-bus within data. Make sure it has naming the container server, with a RollingUpdate rollout strategy, and also needing 64Mi memory, running 4 copies, and with debian:latest as the base image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debian:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""64Mi""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
