283,"Configure a Deployment called data-pipeline in the infra namespace. It should have naming the container main, maintaining 1 pods, additionally using memcached:3.9 as its container image, with env var TIMEOUT assigned to false, and exposing container port 15672.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:3.9""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""false""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: data-pipeline
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: data-pipeline
    team: devops
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: data-pipeline
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: data-pipeline
        team: devops
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: memcached:3.9
        ports:
        - containerPort: 15672
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 512Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 4Gi
        env:
        - name: TIMEOUT
          value: 'false'",Deployment,8
284,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name catalog-api, deployed to infra. Specifications include pulling rabbitmq:3.0, serving on container port 9092, with a replica count of 10, and whose container is called app.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rabbitmq:3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9092""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: catalog-api
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: catalog-api
    version: v2.0
    release: stable
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: catalog-api
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: catalog-api
        version: v2.0
        release: stable
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: rabbitmq:3.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9092
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
        env:
        - name: NODE_ENV
          value: '8080'",Deployment,7
285,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name pdf-generator, deployed to infra. Specifications include the container identified as server, using grafana/grafana:11 as its container image, with container port 5432, scaled to 5 instances.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:11""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5432""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: pdf-generator
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
    env: development
    version: v2.0
    tier: cache
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: pdf-generator
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: pdf-generator
        env: development
        version: v2.0
        tier: cache
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: grafana/grafana:11
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5432",Deployment,7
286,"The user-service-cron CronJob operates in the staging namespace. It has configured with Replace concurrency handling. It is configured with needing 250m of CPU. It features triggered by cron expression 0 0 * * 0. It includes a restart policy of Never. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. It includes naming the container worker.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 * * 0""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""250m""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.concurrencyPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Replace""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: user-service-cron
  namespace: staging
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 * * 0
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: postgres:14
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 250m
                memory: 256Mi
          restartPolicy: Never
  concurrencyPolicy: Replace
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,8
287,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name data-pipeline-svc, deployed to default. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Specifications include with service type ClusterIP, additionally exposing port 9000, additionally communicating over TCP, using ClientIP session affinity.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9000""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: data-pipeline-svc
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: data-pipeline
    tier: frontend
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: cache-proxy
  ports:
  - port: 9000
    targetPort: 9000
    protocol: TCP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,7
288,"We need a ConfigMap named feature-store-config in logging. The configuration requires containing the cache_ttl entry, with max_connections configured as 200, carrying label team: frontend.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""200""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: feature-store-config
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    team: frontend
data:
  max_connections: '200'
  cache_ttl: '300'",ConfigMap,6
289,"Please configure a Pod identified as scheduler-pod within staging. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Make sure it has pulling images with policy Always, additionally exposing port 8200, environment variable JWT_SECRET=info, additionally using httpd:latest as its container image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""httpd:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""info""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8200""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: scheduler-pod
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: scheduler
spec:
  restartPolicy: Always
  containers:
  - name: worker
    image: httpd:latest
    ports:
    - containerPort: 8200
    env:
    - name: JWT_SECRET
      value: info
    imagePullPolicy: Always
  serviceAccountName: monitoring-sa",Pod,7
290,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name file-uploader-config, deployed to monitoring.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: file-uploader-config
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    team: frontend
data:
  redis_host: redis://redis:6379
  app_env: staging
  workers: '8'
  log_level: error
  app_port: '5000'",ConfigMap,3
291,"Provision a Service called batch-processor-svc in the monitoring namespace. It should have as a ClusterIP service, via TCP, and also carrying label env: production, accessible via port 80, matching pods carrying app=worker.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: batch-processor-svc
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: batch-processor
    env: production
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: worker
  ports:
  - port: 80
    targetPort: 8080
    protocol: TCP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,8
292,We need a ConfigMap named scheduler-config in logging.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}]","apiVersion: v1
