293,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name web-app-svc, deployed to staging. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. Specifications include operating as a NodePort service, serving on port 8200.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8200""}]","apiVersion: v1
