304,Please configure a Pod identified as cache-proxy-pod within staging. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. Make sure it has vault:2.0 as its container image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:2.0""}]","apiVersion: v1
