    imagePullPolicy: Always",Pod,4
305,"Please configure a Pod identified as session-store-pod within development. Make sure it has pulling grafana/grafana:stable, with METRICS_PORT configured as 8080, and also exposing port 5432, carrying the app=session-store label, additionally whose container is called app.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:stable""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5432""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: v1
