307,"Deploy a Pod called api-server-pod in the monitoring namespace. It should have declaring the MAX_RETRIES env var, using golang:3.9 as its container image, needing 128Mi memory, labeled app=api-server, listening on port 4222.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:3.9""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""128Mi""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""MAX_RETRIES""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: api-server-pod
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: api-server
    team: ml
spec:
  restartPolicy: Never
  containers:
  - name: app
