308,"Deploy a Pod called analytics-engine-pod in the production namespace. It should have carrying the app=analytics-engine label, using consul:11 as its container image, including LOG_LEVEL in its environment, annotated with tier=database.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""analytics-engine-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""consul:11""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""analytics-engine""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""database""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LOG_LEVEL""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
