309,"Create an Ingress called search-engine-ingress in the development namespace. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. It should have matching /metrics, and responding to requests for auth.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/metrics""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
