              number: 80",Ingress,5
310,"We need a Service named email-sender-svc in default. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. The configuration requires operating as a LoadBalancer service, while also targeting pods with app=log-aggregator, and operating on UDP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator""}]","apiVersion: v1
