311,"Provision an Ingress called config-server-ingress in the production namespace. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. It should have directing traffic for the host shop.example.com, and forwarding requests to the stream-consumer-svc service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""config-server-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""shop.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer-svc""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
