314,The cache-proxy Deployment operates in the ml namespace. It has the API_KEY environment variable. It includes built from busybox:16. It requires its container called app. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. It is configured with maintaining 4 pods. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. It has IfNotPresent image pull policy.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""API_KEY""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""IfNotPresent""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: cache-proxy
    team: infra
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cache-proxy
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cache-proxy
        team: infra
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: busybox:16
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9090
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
        env:
        - name: API_KEY
          value: info",Deployment,8
315,We need a Pod named inventory-svc-pod in data. The configuration requires running busybox:14.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:14""}]","apiVersion: v1
