316,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name gateway-cron, deployed to development. Specifications include scheduled at 0 3 * * 1-5, which is not suspended, annotated with app=pdf-generator, while also executing a command that begins with /bin/sh, and built from grafana/grafana:stable.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 3 * * 1-5""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.command.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/bin/sh""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:stable""}, {""path"": ""spec.suspend"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""False""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: gateway-cron
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
spec:
  schedule: 0 3 * * 1-5
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: grafana/grafana:stable
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - echo hello
          restartPolicy: Never
  concurrencyPolicy: Allow
  suspend: false",CronJob,8
317,"Please configure an Ingress identified as batch-processor-ingress within default. Make sure it has routing /static requests, handling traffic for dashboard.example.com, with TLS using the secret batch-processor-tls, and having the annotation description configured to true.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dashboard.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.secretName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor-tls""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/static""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.description"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: batch-processor-ingress
  namespace: default
  annotations:
    description: 'true'
spec:
  rules:
  - host: dashboard.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /static
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: rate-limiter-svc
            port:
              number: 5000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - dashboard.example.com
    secretName: batch-processor-tls
  ingressClassName: haproxy",Ingress,7
318,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name cache-proxy-ingress, deployed to staging. Specifications include with TLS using the secret cache-proxy-tls, and bound to host api.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.secretName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-tls""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy-ingress
  namespace: staging
  annotations:
    description: 50m
  labels:
    app: cron-runner
spec:
  rules:
  - host: api.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v2
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: backend-svc
            port:
              number: 8080
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - api.example.com
    secretName: cache-proxy-tls
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,5
319,"Configure a Pod called stream-consumer-pod in the default namespace. It should have debian:2.0 as the base image, and also with service account monitoring-sa, and exposing the SECRET_KEY environment variable.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debian:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""SECRET_KEY""}, {""path"": ""spec.serviceAccountName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring-sa""}]","apiVersion: v1
