320,The inventory-svc Deployment operates in the default namespace. It requires needing 100m of CPU. It is configured with running in a container named inventory-svc. It features deployed via RollingUpdate. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. It features pulling prom/prometheus:17. It requires 4 replicas.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:17""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""100m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: inventory-svc
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: inventory-svc
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: inventory-svc
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: inventory-svc
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: inventory-svc
        image: prom/prometheus:17
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9090
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 256Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 64Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: JWT_SECRET
          value: '8080'",Deployment,8
321,The session-store-svc Service operates in the data namespace. It includes forwarding to target port 3306. It has set up as ClusterIP.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3306""}]","apiVersion: v1
