322,The search-engine Deployment operates in the infra namespace. It has having 5 replicated pods. It features the container identified as worker. It includes carrying label tier: monitoring. It features logstash:3.9 as the base image. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. It has tagged as version=v3.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logstash:3.9""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.version"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""v3""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: search-engine
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: search-engine
    tier: monitoring
    version: v3
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: search-engine
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: search-engine
        tier: monitoring
        version: v3
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: logstash:3.9
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3306
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 256Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 64Mi
        env:
        - name: WORKERS
          value: production",Deployment,8
323,The inventory-svc Deployment operates in the monitoring namespace. It has naming the container main. It has kibana:alpine as its container image. It is configured with declaring the DATABASE_URL env var. It has having 1 replicated pods.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""kibana:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""DATABASE_URL""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
