        cpu: 1000m
        memory: 512Mi
    env:
    - name: CACHE_TTL
      value: debug",Pod,4
326,"Set up a CronJob called image-processor-cron in the ml namespace. It should have retaining 3 successful job records, with Never restart behavior, naming the container runner, and also triggered by cron expression */30 * * * *, while also labeled team=devops.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/30 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""devops""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""runner""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: image-processor-cron
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    team: devops
spec:
  schedule: '*/30 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: runner
            image: alpine:5.0
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - date; echo done
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 750m
                memory: 2Gi
          restartPolicy: Never
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 3",CronJob,8
327,The batch-processor-cron CronJob operates in the infra namespace. It is configured with running on schedule */15 * * * *. It features which is not suspended. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. It has restart mode set to Never.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/15 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.suspend"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""False""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: batch-processor-cron
  namespace: infra
spec:
  schedule: '*/15 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: cron
            image: ruby:1.0
          restartPolicy: Never
  suspend: false
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,6
