330,"Create a Deployment called scheduler in the staging namespace. It should have CPU capped at 200m, naming the container app, additionally accepting connections on container port 4222, scaled to 2 instances, using node:11 as its container image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""node:11""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.limits.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""200m""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: scheduler
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: scheduler
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: scheduler
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: scheduler
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: node:11
        ports:
        - containerPort: 4222
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 512Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 2Gi
        env:
        - name: DATABASE_URL
          value: 'false'",Deployment,8
331,The order-service-svc Service operates in the development namespace. It is configured with routing to pods where app is auth-service. It is configured with set up as NodePort. It is configured with serving on port 15672. It requires proxying to port 9200 on the backend.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9200""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}]","apiVersion: v1
