332,The metrics-collector-config ConfigMap operates in the development namespace. It includes containing feature_flags set to beta=true. It includes which includes a timeout_seconds key. It has rate_limit configured as 1000. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. It is configured with where the database_url field is mysql://db:3306/app.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.rate_limit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1000""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta=true""}, {""path"": ""data.database_url"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql://db:3306/app""}]","apiVersion: v1
