338,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name cron-runner-cron, deployed to monitoring. Specifications include set to fire at 30 2 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""30 2 * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
