345,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name search-engine-config, deployed to data. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. Specifications include including a api_key_prefix data key, additionally having the allowed_origins field.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.api_key_prefix"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
