349,"Deploy a ConfigMap called event-bus-config in the development namespace. It should have having feature_flags match the substring ena, mapping app_port to 9090, additionally having app_name=user-service in its data, where the app_name entry includes use, with rate_limit configured as 1000.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""ena""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""use""}, {""path"": ""data.rate_limit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1000""}]","apiVersion: v1
