351,"Please configure a Deployment identified as email-sender within development. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. Make sure it has the container labeled email-sender, additionally pulling redis:5.0, configured with Always pull behavior, running 4 copies, and labeled version=v3.0.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""redis:5.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.version"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""v3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: email-sender
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: email-sender
    version: v3.0
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: email-sender
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: email-sender
        version: v3.0
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: email-sender
        image: redis:5.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: APP_NAME
          value: production",Deployment,8
352,"Provision a Deployment called load-balancer in the default namespace. It should have carrying label env: development, and also built from logstash:2.0, with 8 replicas, additionally naming the container server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""load-balancer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logstash:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: load-balancer
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: load-balancer
    env: development
    version: v3.0
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: load-balancer
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: load-balancer
        env: development
        version: v3.0
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: logstash:2.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3306
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 128Mi
          limits:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 1Gi",Deployment,7
353,"We need a Service named payment-gateway-svc in data. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. The configuration requires session affinity set to ClientIP, matching pods carrying app=order-service, set up as LoadBalancer.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
