376,The image-processor-pod Pod operates in the logging namespace. It has built from openjdk:1.0.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""openjdk:1.0""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
