377,Spin up a Pod called data-pipeline-pod in the development namespace. It should have pulling node:3.9.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""node:3.9""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: data-pipeline-pod
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: data-pipeline
    tier: monitoring
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: runner
    image: node:3.9
