      labels:
        app: batch-processor
        release: blue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: batch-processor
        image: busybox:1.2
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8200
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,7
379,"We need a Deployment named config-server in staging. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. The configuration requires maintaining 6 pods, running grafana/grafana:stable, accepting connections on container port 9092, using the Recreate deployment strategy, and with the container labeled server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""config-server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:stable""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9092""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
