380,Configure a ConfigMap called rate-limiter-config in the platform namespace.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}]","apiVersion: v1
