381,"Please configure a Deployment identified as health-checker within logging. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Make sure it has scaled to 2 instances, and also the container identified as server, built from traefik:slim.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""traefik:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: health-checker
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: health-checker
    team: frontend
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: health-checker
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: health-checker
        team: frontend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: traefik:slim
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
        env:
        - name: APP_NAME
          value: '60'",Deployment,6
382,The worker-svc Service operates in the data namespace. It features configured as NodePort. It features matching pods carrying app=audit-logger.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: worker-svc
  namespace: data
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: audit-logger
  ports:
  - port: 8443
    targetPort: 80
    protocol: UDP",Service,5
383,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name report-gen-ingress, deployed to monitoring. Specifications include bound to host blog.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""blog.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
