  - host: v2.api.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /graphql
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: analytics-engine-svc
            port:
              number: 5000",Ingress,5
431,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name dns-resolver-ingress, deployed to ml. Specifications include having the annotation description configured to /, and also forwarding requests to the log-aggregator-svc service, handling the / endpoint, responding to requests for cdn.example.com, and with a Prefix pathType.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.description"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
