434,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name event-bus-pod, deployed to default. Specifications include using nginx:21 as its container image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nginx:21""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
