443,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name order-service-ingress, deployed to staging. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Specifications include bearing the label app=payment-gateway, responding to requests for blog.example.com, additionally directing traffic to service data-pipeline-svc, and with a Prefix pathType.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""blog.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: order-service-ingress
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: payment-gateway
spec:
  rules:
  - host: blog.example.com
    http:
