461,"Provision a Service called webhook-relay-svc in the ml namespace. It should have proxying to port 4222 on the backend, via UDP, and also matching pods carrying app=user-service, configured as ClusterIP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service""}]","apiVersion: v1
