              number: 443
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - staging.example.com
    secretName: audit-logger-tls
  ingressClassName: haproxy",Ingress,6
495,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name order-service-config, deployed to platform.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: order-service-config
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    team: frontend
data:
  rate_limit: '1000'
  redis_host: redis://redis-master:6379
  app_env: staging
  app_port: '9090'
  feature_flags: enable_v2=true
  workers: '4'",ConfigMap,3
496,The cache-proxy-cron CronJob operates in the monitoring namespace. It requires restart mode set to Never. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. It includes the cron schedule */10 * * * *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/10 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy-cron
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    env: production
spec:
  schedule: '*/10 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: bitnami/kafka:alpine
          restartPolicy: Never
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 3",CronJob,5
497,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name metrics-collector-ingress, deployed to development. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Specifications include serving v2.api.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""v2.api.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
