              number: 5000",Ingress,4
498,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name log-aggregator-ingress, deployed to infra. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Specifications include routing requests to beta.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
