  - name: runner
    image: openjdk:1.1
    ports:
    - containerPort: 9000
    env:
    - name: NODE_ENV
      value: production",Pod,8
501,"We need a Deployment named web-app in staging. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. The configuration requires whose container is called app, having 5 replicated pods, using httpd:11 as its container image, with a CPU request of 1000m.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""httpd:11""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1000m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: web-app
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: web-app
    release: stable
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: web-app
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: web-app
        release: stable
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: httpd:11
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3306
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 1000m
            memory: 256Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,7
502,The backend Deployment operates in the development namespace. It is configured with naming the container worker. It is configured with running bitnami/kafka:1.1. It includes a replica count of 10. It features a Recreate rollout strategy.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:1.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: backend
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: backend
    env: development
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: backend
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: backend
        env: development
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: bitnami/kafka:1.1
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80",Deployment,7
503,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name inventory-svc-svc, deployed to default. Specifications include routing to backend port 11211, and also matching pods carrying app=search-engine, operating as a LoadBalancer service, and also communicating over UDP, configured with ClientIP affinity.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""11211""}]","apiVersion: v1
