505,"Spin up an Ingress called batch-processor-ingress in the staging namespace. It should have serving on port 443, and also routing requests to app.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: batch-processor-ingress
