        - containerPort: 8443",Deployment,7
518,The file-uploader Deployment operates in the default namespace. It has environment variable CACHE_TTL=false. It has prom/prometheus:8 as the base image. It includes running in a container named main. It includes scaled to 10 instances.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""false""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: file-uploader
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: file-uploader
    env: production
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: file-uploader
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: file-uploader
        env: production
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: prom/prometheus:8
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 4Gi
          limits:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 4Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Never
        env:
        - name: CACHE_TTL
          value: 'false'",Deployment,7
519,"Provision an Ingress called pdf-generator-ingress in the development namespace. It should have secured via TLS secret pdf-generator-tls, and also directing traffic to service report-gen-svc, annotated with description set to Ingress, responding to requests for auth.example.com, enabling TLS on auth.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.secretName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator-tls""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.hosts.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.description"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress for pdf-generator-ingress""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: pdf-generator-ingress
  namespace: development
  annotations:
    description: Ingress for pdf-generator-ingress
spec:
  rules:
  - host: auth.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /graphql
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: report-gen-svc
            port:
              number: 3000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - auth.example.com
    secretName: pdf-generator-tls
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,8
520,"We need a Pod named rate-limiter-pod in infra. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. The configuration requires authenticated as service account default, additionally whose container is called main, built from python:21.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:21""}, {""path"": ""spec.serviceAccountName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: rate-limiter-pod
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: rate-limiter
spec:
  restartPolicy: Always
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: python:21
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: 200m
        memory: 128Mi
  serviceAccountName: default",Pod,6
521,"Please configure a Service identified as model-trainer-svc within production. Make sure it has target port set to 9200, accessible at node port 30468, additionally set up as NodePort, and exposing port 8500.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.nodePort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""30468""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9200""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8500""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: model-trainer-svc
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: model-trainer
    team: data
spec:
  type: NodePort
