    nodePort: 30468",Service,7
522,"Please configure a CronJob identified as search-engine-cron within logging. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. Make sure it has allocated 100m CPU, scheduled at 0 3 * * 1-5, and also restart mode set to Never, and which is not suspended.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 3 * * 1-5""}, {""path"": ""spec.suspend"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""False""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""100m""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: search-engine-cron
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    team: devops
spec:
  schedule: 0 3 * * 1-5
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: runner
            image: envoyproxy/envoy:21
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 100m
                memory: 2Gi
          restartPolicy: Never
  suspend: false",CronJob,7
523,"We need a CronJob named image-processor-cron in infra. The configuration requires nats:2.0 as the base image, restarting on Never, and with the cron schedule 0 0 * * 0.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 * * 0""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: image-processor-cron
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    team: infra
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 * * 0
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: job
            image: nats:2.0
            command:
            - python
            - run_job.py
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 1000m
                memory: 2Gi
          restartPolicy: Never
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5",CronJob,6
524,"Please configure an Ingress identified as order-service-ingress within logging. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. Make sure it has bound to host blog.example.com, additionally TLS-secured for blog.example.com, on path /metrics, and also serving on port 3000.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""blog.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3000""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.hosts.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""blog.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/metrics""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: order-service-ingress
  namespace: logging
  annotations:
    description: 50m
spec:
  rules:
  - host: blog.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /metrics
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: stream-consumer-svc
            port:
              number: 3000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - blog.example.com
    secretName: order-service-tls",Ingress,7
525,The load-balancer-ingress Ingress operates in the data namespace. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. It requires serving on port 5000. It features path matching set to Prefix. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. It requires handling the /admin endpoint. It is configured with directing traffic for the host shop.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""load-balancer-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""shop.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/admin""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: load-balancer-ingress
  namespace: data
spec:
  rules:
  - host: shop.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /admin
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: load-balancer-svc
            port:
              number: 5000",Ingress,7
526,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name audit-logger-svc, deployed to development. Specifications include with service type ClusterIP, via UDP, with port 8443 open, and forwarding to target port 9090.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8443""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: audit-logger-svc
  namespace: development
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: auth-service
  ports:
  - port: 8443
    targetPort: 9090
    protocol: UDP",Service,7
527,The worker Deployment operates in the ml namespace. It has vault:4.0 as the base image. It requires naming the container worker. It features maintaining 1 pods.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: worker
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: worker
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: worker
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: worker
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: vault:4.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 11211
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 512Mi",Deployment,6
528,The scheduler Deployment operates in the infra namespace. It includes the Recreate deployment strategy. It requires a replica count of 1. It is configured with the container labeled worker. It requires vault:11 as its container image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:11""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: scheduler
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: scheduler
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: scheduler
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: scheduler
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: vault:11
        ports:
        - containerPort: 15672
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 512Mi
          limits:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 64Mi
        env:
        - name: SECRET_KEY
          value: '8080'",Deployment,7
529,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name rate-limiter-ingress, deployed to staging. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. Specifications include secured via TLS secret rate-limiter-tls, carrying label app: notification-svc, and routing requests to docs.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""docs.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.secretName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-tls""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: rate-limiter-ingress
  namespace: staging
  annotations:
    ssl-redirect: Ingress for rate-limiter-ingress
  labels:
    app: notification-svc
spec:
  rules:
  - host: docs.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /admin
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: frontend-svc
            port:
              number: 5000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - docs.example.com
    secretName: rate-limiter-tls",Ingress,6
530,"Set up a Deployment called report-gen in the platform namespace. It should have tagged as tier=frontend, declaring the DATABASE_URL env var, whose container is called worker, while also built from python:1.2, and with 5 replicas.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:1.2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""DATABASE_URL""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: report-gen
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: report-gen
    tier: frontend
    env: testing
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: report-gen
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: report-gen
        tier: frontend
        env: testing
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: python:1.2
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8500
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 256Mi
        env:
        - name: DATABASE_URL
          value: '8080'",Deployment,8
531,"Please configure a Service identified as data-pipeline-svc within staging. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. Make sure it has of type LoadBalancer, and also forwarding to target port 11211, configured with ClientIP affinity, routing to pods where app is catalog-api, and communicating over UDP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""11211""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: data-pipeline-svc
  namespace: staging
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: catalog-api
  ports:
  - port: 8080
    targetPort: 11211
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,8
532,"Please configure an Ingress identified as report-gen-ingress within default. Make sure it has matching /admin, directing traffic for the host admin.example.com, while also enabling TLS on admin.example.com, accessible via port 80, and routing to backend service model-trainer-svc.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""admin.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/admin""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.hosts.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""admin.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: report-gen-ingress
  namespace: default
spec:
  rules:
  - host: admin.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /admin
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: model-trainer-svc
