548,"Create a Deployment called dns-resolver in the infra namespace. It should have running 5 copies, running bitnami/kafka:11, and whose container is called main.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:11""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: dns-resolver
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: dns-resolver
    tier: queue
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: dns-resolver
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: dns-resolver
        tier: queue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: bitnami/kafka:11
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 1000m
            memory: 1Gi
        env:
        - name: MAX_RETRIES
          value: '8080'",Deployment,6
549,"We need a Service named notification-svc-svc in infra. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. The configuration requires operating on UDP, configured as LoadBalancer, and with port 1883 open.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1883""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: notification-svc-svc
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: notification
    env: staging
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: ssl-terminator
  ports:
  - port: 1883
    targetPort: 4222
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,6
550,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name gateway, deployed to development. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Specifications include naming the container worker, additionally maintaining 6 pods, and pulling centos:stable.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""centos:stable""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
