551,Please configure a Pod identified as queue-worker-pod within logging. Make sure it has based on the python:14 image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""queue-worker-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:14""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: queue-worker-pod
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: queue-worker
spec:
  restartPolicy: Never
  containers:
  - name: runner
