552,"We need a Deployment named cdn-origin in production. The configuration requires based on the grafana/grafana:3.1 image, naming the container worker, with 3 replicas, annotated with tier=monitoring.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:3.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cdn-origin
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: cdn-origin
    tier: monitoring
    version: v1.0
    env: staging
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cdn-origin
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
