556,"Please configure a Service identified as cron-runner-svc within ml. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Make sure it has operating on UDP, additionally set up as ClusterIP, routing to backend port 5432, and forwarding traffic to pods with app=catalog-api.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5432""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}]","apiVersion: v1
