560,"Please configure a Deployment identified as catalog-api within production. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. Make sure it has deployed via Recreate, maintaining 1 pods, and also built from postgres:latest, running in a container named worker, and reserving 50m CPU resources.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""postgres:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50m""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: catalog-api
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: catalog-api
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: catalog-api
