580,"Please configure a CronJob identified as webhook-relay-cron within monitoring. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Make sure it has a restart policy of Never, pulling elasticsearch:3.9, while also executing a command that begins with python, with its container called cron, and also executing on the 0 12 * * * cron schedule.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 12 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.command.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""elasticsearch:3.9""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: webhook-relay-cron
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  schedule: 0 12 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: cron
            image: elasticsearch:3.9
            command:
            - python
            - run_job.py
          restartPolicy: Never
  concurrencyPolicy: Replace
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 3",CronJob,8
581,"Please configure a Deployment identified as auth-service within logging. Make sure it has bitnami/kafka:16 as its container image, naming the container main, and scaled to 4 instances.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: auth-service
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: auth-service
    release: green
    env: testing
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: auth-service
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: auth-service
        release: green
        env: testing
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: bitnami/kafka:16
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 2Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 2Gi
        env:
        - name: SECRET_KEY
          value: '8080'",Deployment,6
582,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name cron-runner-cron, deployed to default. Specifications include naming the container task, while also keeping 5 successful job(s) in history, running on schedule 0 0 * * *, and running httpd:11.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""task""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""httpd:11""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: cron-runner-cron
  namespace: default
  labels:
    env: testing
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: httpd:11
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - echo hello
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 750m
                memory: 512Mi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 2",CronJob,7
583,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name web-app-config, deployed to staging.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}]","apiVersion: v1
