data:
  app_env: production
  app_name: order-service
  log_level: info",ConfigMap,3
584,We need a CronJob named webhook-relay-cron in staging. The configuration requires the cron schedule 0 */2 * * *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */2 * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
