589,"Please configure a Pod identified as audit-logger-pod within development. Make sure it has built from alpine:5.0, restarting on OnFailure, exposing port 1883, and annotated with tier=monitoring.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""alpine:5.0""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1883""}]","apiVersion: v1
