590,The webhook-relay-svc Service operates in the production namespace. It includes service type NodePort. It is configured with target port set to 9200. It requires listening on port 5000. It has routing to pods where app is auth-service.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9200""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}]","apiVersion: v1
