          restartPolicy: Never",CronJob,6
598,The backend Deployment operates in the development namespace. It includes exposing container port 8500. It is configured with employing Recreate for deployments. It requires based on the ruby:slim image. It includes whose container is called main. It has scaled to 2 instances.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8500""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: backend
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: backend
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: backend
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: backend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: ruby:slim
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8500
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 64Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 256Mi",Deployment,8
599,"Configure a Pod called audit-logger-pod in the production namespace. It should have bearing the app label audit-logger, running memcached:latest, and also whose container is called app, setting REDIS_URL to debug, and authenticated as service account app-sa.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:latest""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger""}, {""path"": ""spec.serviceAccountName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app-sa""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debug""}]","apiVersion: v1
