601,"We need a Deployment named metrics-collector in staging. The configuration requires 1 replicas, and also pulling golang:20, and running in a container named metrics-collector.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:20""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
