603,"Please configure a Service identified as cache-proxy-svc within monitoring. Make sure it has set up as ClusterIP, with target port set to 4222.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy-svc
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: health-checker
  ports:
  - port: 9000
    targetPort: 4222
