604,Configure a CronJob called cdn-origin-cron in the development namespace. It should have triggered by cron expression 0 * * * *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 * * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: cdn-origin-cron
  namespace: development
  labels:
    env: development
spec:
  schedule: 0 * * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: cron
            image: alpine:17
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - date; echo done
          restartPolicy: Never
  suspend: false
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 3",CronJob,4
605,"Please configure a Pod identified as rate-limiter-pod within ml. Make sure it has the app label set to rate-limiter, whose container is called app, additionally including WORKERS in its environment, and also having WORKERS set to info, while also based on the nats:1.1 image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:1.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""WORKERS""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""info""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: rate-limiter-pod
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: rate-limiter
    env: production
spec:
  restartPolicy: Always
  containers:
  - name: app
    image: nats:1.1
    ports:
    - containerPort: 11211
    env:
    - name: WORKERS
      value: info",Pod,8
606,"Please configure a Deployment identified as cache-proxy within infra. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Make sure it has configured with Never pull behavior, and also with 3 replicas, running memcached:4.0, and the container identified as server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: cache-proxy
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cache-proxy
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cache-proxy
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: memcached:4.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
        imagePullPolicy: Never
        env:
        - name: WORKERS
          value: '60'",Deployment,7
607,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name auth-service-pod, deployed to production. Specifications include with a restart policy of Always, and also bearing the app label auth-service, running busybox:8, pulling images with policy Never, and tagged as tier=frontend.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:8""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: auth-service-pod
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: auth-service
    tier: frontend
spec:
  restartPolicy: Always
  containers:
  - name: server
    image: busybox:8
    imagePullPolicy: Never",Pod,8
608,"Set up a Pod called scheduler-pod in the default namespace. It should have its container called worker, accessible via port 11211, bearing the app label scheduler, additionally running bitnami/kafka:slim, and restart mode set to OnFailure.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:slim""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""11211""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: scheduler-pod
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: scheduler
    tier: database
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: worker
    image: bitnami/kafka:slim
    ports:
    - containerPort: 11211
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: 250m
        memory: 512Mi",Pod,8
609,The gateway-config ConfigMap operates in the platform namespace. It features storing database_url with value mongodb://mongo:27017/app.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""data.database_url"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongodb://mongo:27017/app""}]","apiVersion: v1
