610,The circuit-breaker-svc Service operates in the monitoring namespace. It is configured with operating as a LoadBalancer service. It has forwarding to target port 5000. It is configured with TCP protocol. It features targeting pods with app=file-uploader.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""circuit-breaker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}]","apiVersion: v1
