612,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name scheduler-pod, deployed to logging. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. Specifications include based on the envoyproxy/envoy:3.0 image, and whose container is called app.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""envoyproxy/envoy:3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: v1
