614,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name ssl-terminator-svc, deployed to production. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. Specifications include with service type LoadBalancer, selecting pods labeled app=proxy-server, via UDP, and listening on port 9090.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""proxy-server""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: ssl-terminator-svc
  namespace: production
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: proxy-server
  ports:
  - port: 9090
    targetPort: 9200
    protocol: UDP",Service,7
615,"We need a Deployment named frontend in production. The configuration requires based on the memcached:21 image, annotated with version=v2, with a memory request of 512Mi, whose container is called main, while also running 2 copies.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:21""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""512Mi""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.version"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""v2""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: frontend
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: frontend
    version: v2
    tier: database
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: frontend
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: frontend
        version: v2
        tier: database
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: memcached:21
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5432
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 512Mi
          limits:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 64Mi",Deployment,8
616,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name feature-store-cron, deployed to infra. Specifications include with the cron schedule */15 * * * *, additionally naming the container runner, and also launching with the /bin/sh command prefix, and needing 500m of CPU.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/15 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""500m""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""runner""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.command.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/bin/sh""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: feature-store-cron
  namespace: infra
spec:
  schedule: '*/15 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: runner
            image: python:2.0
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - echo hello
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 500m
                memory: 1Gi
          restartPolicy: Never
  concurrencyPolicy: Forbid",CronJob,7
617,The ssl-terminator-ingress Ingress operates in the platform namespace. It has directing traffic to service load-balancer-svc. It requires path matching set to Exact. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. It features responding to requests for admin.example.com. It features having the annotation ssl-redirect configured to true.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""admin.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Exact""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""load-balancer-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.ssl-redirect"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: ssl-terminator-ingress
  namespace: platform
  annotations:
    ssl-redirect: 'true'
spec:
  rules:
  - host: admin.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /docs
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: load-balancer-svc
            port:
              number: 3000",Ingress,7
618,The inventory-svc Deployment operates in the infra namespace. It has pulling golang:3.0. It is configured with allocated 50m CPU. It has the container identified as app. It is configured with 2 replicas.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: inventory-svc
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: inventory-svc
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: inventory-svc
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: inventory-svc
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: golang:3.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3306
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 64Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 64Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,7
619,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name auth-service-pod, deployed to staging. Specifications include restarting on Always, built from mongo:8.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongo:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}]","apiVersion: v1
