  - host: shop.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v1
        pathType: ImplementationSpecific
        backend:
          service:
            name: model-trainer-svc
            port:
              number: 443
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - shop.example.com
    secretName: backend-tls
  ingressClassName: traefik",Ingress,4
636,"Set up a Service called api-server-svc in the ml namespace. It should have targeting port 15672, set up as NodePort, exposing port 9090, and also via TCP, and labeled env=production.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: api-server-svc
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: api-server
    env: production
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: api-server
  ports:
  - port: 9090
    targetPort: 15672
    protocol: TCP
    nodePort: 32545",Service,8
637,"Provision a Deployment called notification-svc in the logging namespace. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. It should have needing 2 of CPU, additionally exposing the TIMEOUT environment variable, running python:3.1, running in a container named worker, having 8 replicated pods.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:3.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TIMEOUT""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: notification-svc
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: notification-svc
    team: frontend
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: notification-svc
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: notification-svc
        team: frontend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: python:3.1
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 4Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 256Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: TIMEOUT
          value: '3'",Deployment,8
638,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name model-trainer-ingress, deployed to infra. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. Specifications include with port 8080 open, bound to host dashboard.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dashboard.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: model-trainer-ingress
  namespace: infra
spec:
  rules:
  - host: dashboard.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /admin
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: image-processor-svc
            port:
              number: 8080
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,5
639,"We need a Pod named frontend-pod in infra. The configuration requires labeled app=frontend, listening on port 5000, with mysql:11 as the base image, naming the container runner, and with Always restart behavior.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql:11""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""runner""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: frontend-pod
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: frontend
    team: data
spec:
  restartPolicy: Always
  containers:
  - name: runner
    image: mysql:11
    ports:
    - containerPort: 5000
    env:
    - name: WORKERS
      value: production",Pod,8
640,"Please configure a CronJob identified as frontend-cron within infra. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. Make sure it has restart policy Never, and also executing on the 0 0 1 * * cron schedule, the container identified as cron, and also bearing the label env=staging, and which is not suspended.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 1 * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.suspend"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""False""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: frontend-cron
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    env: staging
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 1 * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: cron
            image: logstash:latest
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 250m
                memory: 1Gi
          restartPolicy: Never
  concurrencyPolicy: Replace
  suspend: false",CronJob,8
641,"Deploy a Service called rate-limiter-svc in the infra namespace. It should have annotated with tier=cache, and set up as NodePort.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache""}]","apiVersion: v1
