642,Please configure a CronJob identified as metrics-collector-cron within staging. Make sure it has the cron schedule 0 */2 * * *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */2 * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
