643,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name cdn-origin, deployed to data. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. Specifications include with the container labeled cdn-origin, with 1 replicas, where CACHE_TTL equals production, and also based on the bitnami/kafka:4.0 image, and with CACHE_TTL defined in its environment.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CACHE_TTL""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
