    - name: DEBUG
      value: info
    imagePullPolicy: Never",Pod,6
667,"We need a Pod named inventory-svc-pod in production. The configuration requires carrying the app=inventory-svc label, environment variable DEBUG=8080, carrying label tier: backend, based on the postgres:4.0 image, and restart mode set to OnFailure.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""postgres:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: inventory-svc-pod
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: inventory-svc
    tier: backend
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: app
