686,"Please configure a Deployment identified as session-store within logging. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. Make sure it has the version label set to v2.0, naming the container main, scaled to 2 instances, and also with the team label set to backend, pulling golang:latest.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.version"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""v2.0""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: session-store
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: session-store
    version: v2.0
    tier: queue
    team: backend
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: session-store
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: session-store
        version: v2.0
        tier: queue
        team: backend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: golang:latest
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
        env:
        - name: DEBUG
          value: info",Deployment,8
687,"We need a Deployment named event-bus in platform. The configuration requires mongo:1.1 as its container image, and also with its container called event-bus, running 6 copies.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongo:1.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: event-bus
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: event-bus
    release: green
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: event-bus
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: event-bus
        release: green
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: event-bus
        image: mongo:1.1
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 2Gi",Deployment,6
688,"We need a Deployment named file-uploader in logging. The configuration requires pulling ruby:16, the container identified as app, and having 2 replicated pods.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:16""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: file-uploader
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: file-uploader
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: file-uploader
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: file-uploader
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
