  serviceAccountName: admin",Pod,4
731,"We need a Service named notification-svc-svc in monitoring. The configuration requires ClientIP session affinity, and also forwarding to target port 3000, and also with service type NodePort, with port 15672 open, additionally operating on TCP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3000""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: notification-svc-svc
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: file-uploader
  ports:
  - port: 15672
    targetPort: 3000
    protocol: TCP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,8
732,The ssl-terminator-svc Service operates in the staging namespace. It requires forwarding to target port 80. It is configured with of type LoadBalancer.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: ssl-terminator-svc
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: ssl-terminator
    env: testing
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: catalog-api
  ports:
  - port: 8443
    targetPort: 80
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,5
733,"Configure a Pod called email-sender-pod in the default namespace. It should have nats:3.1 as its container image, additionally with the app label set to email-sender, accepting traffic on port 27017, with OnFailure restart behavior.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:3.1""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""27017""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: email-sender-pod
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: email-sender
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: worker
