  name: email-sender-pod
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: email-sender
spec:
  restartPolicy: Never
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: logstash:16",Pod,4
796,We need a ConfigMap named auth-service-config in default. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}]","apiVersion: v1
