797,"Please configure a CronJob identified as frontend-cron within logging. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. Make sure it has OnFailure restart behavior, triggered by cron expression 0 12 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 12 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: frontend-cron
  namespace: logging
spec:
  schedule: 0 12 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: postgres:8
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 1
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 2",CronJob,5
798,"Spin up an Ingress called file-uploader-ingress in the production namespace. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. It should have handling traffic for shop.example.com, and also with path matching set to Prefix.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""shop.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: file-uploader-ingress
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: order-service
spec:
  rules:
  - host: shop.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v2
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: health-checker-svc
            port:
              number: 80",Ingress,5
799,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name auth-service-cron, deployed to platform. Specifications include with the cron schedule 0 12 * * *, with its command starting with /bin/sh, and also keeping 5 successful job(s) in history, the container identified as worker.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 12 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.command.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/bin/sh""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: auth-service-cron
  namespace: platform
spec:
  schedule: 0 12 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: ruby:5.0
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - date; echo done
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  suspend: false
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5",CronJob,7
800,"Deploy a Pod called gateway-pod in the logging namespace. It should have needing 1000m of CPU, running elasticsearch:1.0, with its container called main.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""elasticsearch:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1000m""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: gateway-pod
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: gateway
    env: staging
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: elasticsearch:1.0
    ports:
    - containerPort: 8080
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: 1000m
        memory: 2Gi
    env:
    - name: SECRET_KEY
      value: debug
    imagePullPolicy: Always",Pod,6
801,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name ssl-terminator-svc, deployed to data. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. Specifications include operating on UDP, and set up as ClusterIP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: ssl-terminator-svc
  namespace: data
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: cache-proxy
  ports:
  - port: 9092
    targetPort: 443
    protocol: UDP",Service,5
802,"Create a Deployment called dns-resolver in the production namespace. It should have running grafana/grafana:3.0, bearing the label tier=backend, having 3 replicated pods, where DATABASE_URL equals false, with its container called main.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""false""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: dns-resolver
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: dns-resolver
    tier: backend
    env: testing
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: dns-resolver
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: dns-resolver
        tier: backend
        env: testing
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: grafana/grafana:3.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9092
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 128Mi
        env:
        - name: DATABASE_URL
          value: 'false'",Deployment,8
803,The gateway-pod Pod operates in the monitoring namespace. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. It is configured with ubuntu:3.1 as the base image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ubuntu:3.1""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: gateway-pod
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: gateway
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: app
    image: ubuntu:3.1
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: 100m
        memory: 1Gi
    env:
    - name: METRICS_PORT
      value: '8080'
    imagePullPolicy: Never
  serviceAccountName: app-sa",Pod,4
804,"We need a Pod named event-bus-pod in platform. The configuration requires carrying the app=event-bus label, while also exposing port 6379, and also pulling vault:alpine, needing 2 of CPU.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6379""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: event-bus-pod
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: event-bus
    env: staging
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: vault:alpine
    ports:
    - containerPort: 6379
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: '2'
        memory: 128Mi
    env:
    - name: NODE_ENV
      value: info",Pod,7
805,The service-mesh Deployment operates in the staging namespace. It features having 10 replicated pods. It is configured with pulling bitnami/kafka:2.0. It has a Recreate rollout strategy. It requires running in a container named server.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""service-mesh""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: service-mesh
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: service-mesh
    env: production
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: service-mesh
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: service-mesh
        env: production
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: bitnami/kafka:2.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 11211
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 2Gi
        env:
        - name: NODE_ENV
          value: '3'",Deployment,7
806,"Please configure a CronJob identified as dns-resolver-cron within logging. Make sure it has restart mode set to Never, with concurrency policy Replace, and also with its container called task, while also running on schedule 0 12 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 12 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.concurrencyPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Replace""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""task""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: dns-resolver-cron
  namespace: logging
spec:
  schedule: 0 12 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: redis:3.1
          restartPolicy: Never
  concurrencyPolicy: Replace",CronJob,7
807,The notification-svc-pod Pod operates in the staging namespace. It features ruby:4.0 as the base image. It is configured with JWT_SECRET configured as production. It is configured with imagePullPolicy set to Never.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: notification-svc-pod
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: notification-svc
    tier: backend
spec:
  restartPolicy: Always
  containers:
  - name: app
    image: ruby:4.0
    ports:
    - containerPort: 8500
    env:
    - name: JWT_SECRET
      value: production
    imagePullPolicy: Never",Pod,6
808,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name metrics-collector, deployed to logging. Specifications include with the container labeled main, additionally built from prom/prometheus:slim, while also with 5 replicas.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: metrics-collector
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: metrics-collector
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: metrics-collector
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: metrics-collector
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: prom/prometheus:slim
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 256Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 128Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always",Deployment,6
809,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name payment-gateway, deployed to monitoring. Specifications include scaled to 6 instances, additionally declaring the APP_NAME env var, using elasticsearch:17 as its container image, whose container is called payment-gateway.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""elasticsearch:17""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""APP_NAME""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: payment-gateway
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: payment-gateway
    env: staging
    version: v2.1
    tier: database
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: payment-gateway
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: payment-gateway
        env: staging
        version: v2.1
        tier: database
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: payment-gateway
        image: elasticsearch:17
        ports:
        - containerPort: 1883
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 2Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: APP_NAME
          value: 'false'",Deployment,7
810,"Please configure a Deployment identified as gateway within logging. Make sure it has running 1 copies, and also with consul:17 as the base image, while also the container identified as gateway, and exposing the TIMEOUT environment variable.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""consul:17""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TIMEOUT""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: gateway
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: gateway
    env: testing
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: gateway
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: gateway
        env: testing
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: gateway
        image: consul:17
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80
        env:
        - name: TIMEOUT
          value: '8080'",Deployment,7
811,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name search-engine, deployed to platform. Specifications include running 4 copies, with the container labeled worker, with consul:1.0 as the base image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""consul:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: search-engine
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: search-engine
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: search-engine
  strategy:
