  name: cache-proxy-config
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    team: ml
data:
  app_port: '3000'
  rate_limit: '100'
  log_level: info
  retry_count: '5'",ConfigMap,6
824,The search-engine-svc Service operates in the data namespace. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. It includes service type NodePort.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: search-engine-svc
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: search-engine
    tier: database
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: health-checker
  ports:
  - port: 3306
    targetPort: 3306
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,4
825,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name service-mesh-config, deployed to logging. Specifications include mapping max_connections to 500.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""service-mesh-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""500""}]","apiVersion: v1
