826,"Please configure a Pod identified as auth-service-pod within data. Make sure it has Never restart behavior, with the container labeled main, and also running python:3.0.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: v1
