838,The worker-config ConfigMap operates in the staging namespace. It features log_level configured as warn. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. It has including a rate_limit data key.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""data.rate_limit"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.log_level"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""warn""}]","apiVersion: v1
