840,"We need a Service named log-aggregator-svc in production. The configuration requires as a ClusterIP service, and also accepting traffic on port 3000.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3000""}]","apiVersion: v1
