842,"We need a Service named notification-svc-svc in data. The configuration requires matching pods carrying app=order-service, additionally targeting port 15672, with service type NodePort.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}]","apiVersion: v1
