843,"Please configure a Service identified as feature-store-svc within default. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Make sure it has accepting traffic on port 443, additionally operating as a LoadBalancer service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}]","apiVersion: v1
