844,"Please configure an Ingress identified as notification-svc-ingress within default. Make sure it has tagged as app=ml-inference, accepting traffic on port 80, directing traffic to service cache-proxy-svc, additionally serving staging.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-svc""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
