846,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name model-trainer-ingress, deployed to ml. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Specifications include backed by service notification-svc-svc, additionally serving ws.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ws.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-svc""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
