            port:
              number: 5000",Ingress,5
847,"Spin up a CronJob called cache-proxy-cron in the data namespace. It should have OnFailure restart behavior, additionally needing 250m of CPU, with the cron schedule 0 */2 * * *, with busybox:14 as the base image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */2 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""250m""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy-cron
  namespace: data
spec:
  schedule: 0 */2 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: busybox:14
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - cleanup.sh
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 250m
                memory: 1Gi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  suspend: false
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5",CronJob,7
848,"We need a CronJob named metrics-collector-cron in staging. The configuration requires Allow concurrency, based on the debian:1.0 image, additionally running on schedule 0 */6 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */6 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.concurrencyPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Allow""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debian:1.0""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: metrics-collector-cron
  namespace: staging
spec:
  schedule: 0 */6 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: job
            image: debian:1.0
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  concurrencyPolicy: Allow
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,6
849,The worker-config ConfigMap operates in the staging namespace. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. It features where the workers field is 8.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""data.workers"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: worker-config
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    env: production
data:
  workers: '8'
  log_level: error
  database_url: mysql://db:3306/app
  debug_mode: 'true'",ConfigMap,4
850,"Provision a Deployment called notification-svc in the logging namespace. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. It should have running bitnami/kafka:1.1, running 8 copies, and naming the container server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:1.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: notification-svc
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: notification-svc
    tier: monitoring
    env: staging
spec:
  replicas: 8
