863,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name auth-service-ingress, deployed to infra. Specifications include capturing requests to /api/v1, routing requests to beta.example.com, directing traffic to service order-service-svc, carrying annotation ssl-redirect: Ingress.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.ssl-redirect"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress for auth-service-ingress""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/api/v1""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-svc""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
