921,The cron-runner-config ConfigMap operates in the ml namespace. It has containing the feature_flags entry. It requires having retry_count=3 in its data. It requires storing feature_flags with value enable_v2=true. It requires having the app_port field. It has app_port configured as 3000.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3000""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""enable_v2=true""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.retry_count"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: cron-runner-config
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    env: production
data:
  feature_flags: enable_v2=true
  app_port: '3000'
  retry_count: '3'
  workers: '8'
  cache_ttl: '600'",ConfigMap,8
922,"Create a Deployment called metrics-collector in the ml namespace. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. It should have having 2 replicated pods, with the container labeled app, reserving 1000m CPU resources, using vault:14 as its container image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1000m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: metrics-collector
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: metrics-collector
    release: green
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: metrics-collector
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: metrics-collector
        release: green
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: vault:14
        ports:
        - containerPort: 4222
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 1000m
            memory: 512Mi
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent
        env:
        - name: NODE_ENV
          value: '8080'",Deployment,7
923,"Please configure a ConfigMap identified as user-service-config within monitoring. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. Make sure it has mapping max_connections to 500, additionally with database_url containing the text mon, having the max_connections field, additionally having database_url=mongodb://mongo:27017/app in its data.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.database_url"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongodb://mongo:27017/app""}, {""path"": ""data.database_url"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""mon""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""500""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: user-service-config
  namespace: monitoring
data:
  database_url: mongodb://mongo:27017/app
  max_connections: '500'
  timeout_seconds: '5'",ConfigMap,7
924,Configure an Ingress called model-trainer-ingress in the infra namespace. It should have serving cdn.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: model-trainer-ingress
  namespace: infra
  annotations:
    proxy-body-size: /
spec:
  rules:
  - host: cdn.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v1
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: ssl-terminator-svc
