  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,4
925,"We need a CronJob named ssl-terminator-cron in monitoring. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. The configuration requires executing a command that begins with curl, while also with a restart policy of Never, additionally allocated 50m CPU, triggered by cron expression 0 3 * * 1-5, and with its container called task.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 3 * * 1-5""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50m""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""task""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.command.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""curl""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: ssl-terminator-cron
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  schedule: 0 3 * * 1-5
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: prom/prometheus:stable
            command:
            - curl
            - -s
            - http://api/health
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 50m
                memory: 64Mi
          restartPolicy: Never",CronJob,8
926,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name log-aggregator-svc, deployed to data. Specifications include as a LoadBalancer service, while also operating on UDP, matching pods carrying app=proxy-server, listening on port 5432, and forwarding to target port 9200.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""proxy-server""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9200""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5432""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: log-aggregator-svc
  namespace: data
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: proxy-server
  ports:
  - port: 5432
    targetPort: 9200
    protocol: UDP",Service,8
927,"We need a Deployment named api-server in production. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. The configuration requires having 10 replicated pods, based on the busybox:1.0 image, while also annotated with tier=monitoring, and with the container labeled main.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: api-server
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: api-server
    tier: monitoring
    env: production
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: api-server
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: api-server
        tier: monitoring
        env: production
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: busybox:1.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5432
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 64Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,7
928,The file-uploader-pod Pod operates in the infra namespace. It includes configuring the API_KEY variable. It requires where API_KEY equals true. It features the container identified as app. It includes restarting on Always. It is configured with grafana/grafana:3.9 as the base image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:3.9""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""API_KEY""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}]","apiVersion: v1
