931,The email-sender-pod Pod operates in the logging namespace. It is configured with tagged as team=platform. It requires built from openjdk:slim. It is configured with listening on port 5000. It requires restarting on Never.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""openjdk:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}]","apiVersion: v1
