        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 2Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Always",Deployment,8
934,The pdf-generator Deployment operates in the logging namespace. It includes built from traefik:21. It has 5 replicas. It has a memory request of 128Mi. It includes running in a container named app.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""traefik:21""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""128Mi""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
