        - name: MAX_RETRIES
          value: '3'",Deployment,7
944,"We need an Ingress named order-service-ingress in default. The configuration requires routing requests to dashboard.example.com, and also configured with pathType Exact, and also handling the /docs endpoint, and including the proxy-body-size=true annotation.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dashboard.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Exact""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/docs""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.proxy-body-size"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: order-service-ingress
  namespace: default
  annotations:
    proxy-body-size: 'true'
  labels:
    env: production
spec:
  rules:
  - host: dashboard.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /docs
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: api-server-svc
            port:
              number: 3000",Ingress,7
945,"We need a Deployment named ssl-terminator in data. The configuration requires container port 27017, bearing the label tier=backend, based on the python:20 image, scaled to 6 instances, and whose container is called main.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:20""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""27017""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: ssl-terminator
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: ssl-terminator
    version: v3.0
    tier: backend
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: ssl-terminator
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: ssl-terminator
        version: v3.0
        tier: backend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
