        ports:
        - containerPort: 27017
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 4Gi",Deployment,8
946,"We need a ConfigMap named pdf-generator-config in development. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. The configuration requires containing feature_flags set to enable_v2=true, containing app_port set to 9090, including a app_port data key, and where the allowed_origins entry includes htt.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""htt""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""enable_v2=true""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: pdf-generator-config
  namespace: development
data:
  app_port: '9090'
  feature_flags: enable_v2=true
  timeout_seconds: '30'
  log_level: error
  allowed_origins: https://example.com",ConfigMap,7
947,The log-aggregator-ingress Ingress operates in the logging namespace. It requires listening on port 8080. It includes handling traffic for staging.example.com. It features handling the /api endpoint.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/api""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: log-aggregator-ingress
  namespace: logging
spec:
  rules:
  - host: staging.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api
        pathType: ImplementationSpecific
        backend:
          service:
            name: image-processor-svc
            port:
              number: 8080
  ingressClassName: traefik",Ingress,6
948,"Create a Deployment called auth-service in the logging namespace. It should have the container identified as worker, and also running 4 copies, and built from nats:5.0.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:5.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: auth-service
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: auth-service
    version: v2.0
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: auth-service
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: auth-service
        version: v2.0
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: nats:5.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 128Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 128Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always",Deployment,6
949,"Please configure a CronJob identified as auth-service-cron within ml. Make sure it has built from debian:20, tagged as app=backend, whose container is called cron, while also which is not suspended, with the cron schedule */30 * * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/30 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debian:20""}, {""path"": ""spec.suspend"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""False""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: auth-service-cron
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: backend
spec:
  schedule: '*/30 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: cron
            image: debian:20
          restartPolicy: Never
  suspend: false",CronJob,8
950,Configure a ConfigMap called backend-config in the production namespace. It should have mapping timeout_seconds to 10.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}]","apiVersion: v1
