    env:
    - name: MAX_RETRIES
      value: 'true'",Pod,6
960,The order-service Deployment operates in the infra namespace. It has having 2 replicated pods. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. It requires where APP_NAME equals true. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. It requires naming the container main. It requires pulling nats:8.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: order-service
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: order-service
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: order-service
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: order-service
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: nats:8
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 64Mi
        env:
        - name: APP_NAME
          value: 'true'",Deployment,7
961,The cron-runner-pod Pod operates in the platform namespace. It has a restart policy of OnFailure. It includes bearing the app label cron-runner. It features the container labeled server. It requires running node:alpine.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""node:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner""}]","apiVersion: v1
