962,"Please configure an Ingress identified as notification-svc-ingress within ml. Make sure it has responding to requests for shop.example.com, and including the proxy-body-size=/ annotation.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""shop.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.proxy-body-size"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
