963,"Please configure a Pod identified as order-service-pod within platform. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Make sure it has built from nats:3.1, labeled app=order-service, and annotated with env=staging.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:3.1""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service""}]","apiVersion: v1
