metadata:
  name: email-sender-cron
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: analytics-engine
spec:
  schedule: 0 */2 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: memcached:1.1
          restartPolicy: OnFailure",CronJob,5
998,Please configure a ConfigMap identified as circuit-breaker-config within default. The team responsible for this resource can be reached via the platform-ops Slack channel.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""circuit-breaker-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: circuit-breaker-config
  namespace: default
  labels:
    team: ml
data:
  rate_limit: '5000'
  feature_flags: enable_v2=true
  debug_mode: 'true'
  max_connections: '100'",ConfigMap,3
999,"Configure a Deployment called session-store in the development namespace. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. It should have opening container port 3306, maintaining 10 pods, additionally running in a container named session-store, additionally pulling httpd:5.0.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""httpd:5.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3306""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: session-store
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: session-store
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: session-store
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: session-store
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: session-store
        image: httpd:5.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3306
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent",Deployment,7
1000,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name report-gen-svc, deployed to staging. Specifications include carrying label env: staging, while also operating as a LoadBalancer service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}]","apiVersion: v1
