1001,"We need a Deployment named dns-resolver in production. The configuration requires maintaining 2 pods, and also the container should share the same name as the resource itself, and with busybox:alpine as the base image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""busybox:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: dns-resolver
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: dns-resolver
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: dns-resolver
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: dns-resolver
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: dns-resolver
        image: busybox:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 15672",Deployment,6
1002,The cdn-origin-ingress Ingress operates in the monitoring namespace. It features handling traffic for admin.example.com. It features port 443 open. It includes routing to backend service payment-gateway-svc. It has matching /static. It includes configured with pathType ImplementationSpecific.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""admin.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ImplementationSpecific""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/static""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway-svc""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: cdn-origin-ingress
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  rules:
  - host: admin.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /static
        pathType: ImplementationSpecific
        backend:
          service:
            name: payment-gateway-svc
            port:
              number: 443",Ingress,8
1003,"Create a Deployment called payment-gateway in the default namespace. It should have prom/prometheus:2.0 as its container image, and also with a memory request of 1Gi, with 3 replicas, and running in a container named server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1Gi""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: payment-gateway
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: payment-gateway
    release: green
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: payment-gateway
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: payment-gateway
        release: green
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: prom/prometheus:2.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8200
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 1Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: JWT_SECRET
          value: '3'",Deployment,7
1004,Create a Pod called webhook-relay-pod in the platform namespace. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. It should have pulling mongo:3.9.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongo:3.9""}]","apiVersion: v1
