1007,"We need a CronJob named event-bus-cron in logging. The configuration requires restart mode set to Never, while also with its container called worker, and also scheduled at 30 2 * * *, additionally annotated with team=data, using vault:1.2 as its container image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""30 2 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:1.2""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: event-bus-cron
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    team: data
spec:
  schedule: 30 2 * * *
  jobTemplate:
