1010,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name health-checker-config, deployed to platform. Specifications include mapping max_connections to 500, and also having log_level=debug in its data, which includes a max_connections key, while also storing cache_ttl with value 300.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""data.log_level"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debug""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""500""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""300""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
