1011,"We need a CronJob named event-bus-cron in production. The configuration requires which is not suspended, while also retaining 1 failed job records, additionally the container identified as runner, while also with the cron schedule 0 0 * * *, and with debian:slim as the base image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""runner""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""debian:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.suspend"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""False""}, {""path"": ""spec.failedJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: event-bus-cron
  namespace: production
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: runner
            image: debian:slim
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - cleanup.sh
          restartPolicy: Never
  suspend: false
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,8
1012,The ml-inference-ingress Ingress operates in the infra namespace. It requires the ml-inference-tls TLS secret. It includes routing to backend service frontend-svc. It requires directing traffic for the host status.example.com. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. It is configured with TLS termination on status.example.com. It features serving on port 80.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""status.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.secretName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-tls""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.hosts.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""status.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: ml-inference-ingress
  namespace: infra
spec:
  rules:
  - host: status.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v1
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: frontend-svc
            port:
              number: 80
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - status.example.com
    secretName: ml-inference-tls
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,8
1013,"Provision a Service called model-trainer-svc in the infra namespace. It should have routing to backend port 9200, additionally serving on port 9092, while also targeting pods with app=session-store, operating as a ClusterIP service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9200""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9092""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: model-trainer-svc
  namespace: infra
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: session-store
  ports:
  - port: 9092
    targetPort: 9200
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,7
1014,Please configure a Pod identified as backend-pod within development. Make sure it has pulling rabbitmq:3.1.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rabbitmq:3.1""}]","apiVersion: v1
