1015,"We need an Ingress named backend-ingress in staging. The configuration requires labeled app=frontend, routing requests to shop.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""shop.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
