1016,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name payment-gateway-cron, deployed to infra. Specifications include set to fire at 0 */6 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */6 * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
