            command:
            - python
            - run_job.py
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  concurrencyPolicy: Replace",CronJob,4
1017,The pdf-generator Deployment operates in the logging namespace. It features built from grafana/grafana:14. It requires 4 replicas. It includes exposing the LOG_LEVEL environment variable. It includes the container labeled app.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana/grafana:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LOG_LEVEL""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: pdf-generator
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
    version: v3
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: pdf-generator
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: pdf-generator
        version: v3
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: grafana/grafana:14
        ports:
        - containerPort: 27017
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 128Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: LOG_LEVEL
          value: '60'",Deployment,7
1018,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name cron-runner-svc, deployed to production. Specifications include operating as a ClusterIP service, exposing port 5000, and via TCP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cron-runner-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
