  name: cron-runner-svc
  namespace: production
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: stream-consumer
  ports:
  - port: 5000
    targetPort: 6379
    protocol: TCP",Service,6
1019,The load-balancer-ingress Ingress operates in the production namespace. It has handling traffic for status.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""load-balancer-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""status.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
