1020,"Provision a Pod called gateway-pod in the data namespace. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. It should have the app label set to gateway, and pulling openjdk:8.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""openjdk:8""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: gateway-pod
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: gateway
spec:
  restartPolicy: Always
  containers:
  - name: worker
    image: openjdk:8
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: '1'
        memory: 128Mi
    env:
    - name: LOG_LEVEL
      value: '8080'
    imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent",Pod,5
1021,Deploy a Pod called image-processor-pod in the logging namespace. It should have built from redis:8.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""redis:8""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: image-processor-pod
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: image-processor
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: worker
    image: redis:8
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: 1000m
        memory: 1Gi
    env:
    - name: REDIS_URL
      value: 'true'
  serviceAccountName: monitoring-sa",Pod,4
1022,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name notification-svc, deployed to development. Specifications include with the container labeled notification-svc, running envoyproxy/envoy:stable, and having 3 replicated pods.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""envoyproxy/envoy:stable""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
