1023,The log-aggregator-pod Pod operates in the ml namespace. It includes logstash:11 as the base image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logstash:11""}]","apiVersion: v1
