1024,We need a Pod named catalog-api-pod in development. This was previously hosted on AWS ECS before the Kubernetes migration. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. The configuration requires httpd:14 as its container image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""httpd:14""}]","apiVersion: v1
