    - name: WORKERS
      value: 'false'",Pod,4
1025,The ssl-terminator-pod Pod operates in the default namespace. It is configured with vault:slim as the base image. It requires carrying the app=ssl-terminator label. It requires its container called server. It requires OnFailure restart behavior. It features bearing the label tier=cache.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache""}]","apiVersion: v1
