1026,"The search-engine-svc Service operates in the development namespace. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. It is configured with set up as ClusterIP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
