        cpu: 750m
        memory: 128Mi",Pod,6
1028,The event-bus Deployment operates in the default namespace. It is configured with running golang:2.0. It features running in a container named app. It is configured with a Recreate rollout strategy. It requires container port 443. It is configured with having 1 replicated pods.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: event-bus
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: event-bus
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: event-bus
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: event-bus
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: golang:2.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 4Gi
        env:
        - name: JWT_SECRET
          value: production",Deployment,8
1029,"We need a ConfigMap named user-service-config in development. The configuration requires mapping max_connections to 10, additionally mapping rate_limit to 5000, and also containing the max_connections entry, mapping debug_mode to true, and containing timeout_seconds set to 5.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""data.debug_mode"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""data.rate_limit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: user-service-config
  namespace: development
data:
  app_name: auth-service
  max_connections: '10'
  debug_mode: 'true'
  workers: '4'
  rate_limit: '5000'
  timeout_seconds: '5'",ConfigMap,8
1030,"Set up a Service called backend-svc in the production namespace. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. It should have targeting pods with app=auth-service, additionally with service type NodePort, forwarding to target port 3306, and listening on port 27017.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""27017""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3306""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: backend-svc
  namespace: production
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: auth-service
  ports:
  - port: 27017
    targetPort: 3306
    protocol: UDP
  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,7
1031,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Pod with name session-store-pod, deployed to monitoring. Specifications include reserving 256Mi of memory, and also labeled app=session-store, additionally using restart policy Never, tagged as env=testing, and built from envoyproxy/envoy:8.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""envoyproxy/envoy:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""256Mi""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""testing""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: session-store-pod
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: session-store
    env: testing
spec:
  restartPolicy: Never
  containers:
