1033,"Provision an Ingress called health-checker-ingress in the ml namespace. It should have tagged as env=production, directing traffic for the host v2.api.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""v2.api.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
