              number: 443",Ingress,5
1034,"Configure a Service called user-service-svc in the development namespace. It should have of type LoadBalancer, while also forwarding to target port 8500, routing to pods where app is data-pipeline, using TCP protocol, and with port 8200 open.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8200""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8500""}]","apiVersion: v1
