              number: 8080",Ingress,6
1036,"We need a CronJob named data-pipeline-cron in monitoring. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. The configuration requires requesting 2 CPU, set to fire at 0 12 * * *, while also pulling python:4.0, additionally preserving the last 1 successful runs, with concurrency policy Forbid.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 12 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.concurrencyPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Forbid""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: data-pipeline-cron
  namespace: monitoring
spec:
  schedule: 0 12 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: python:4.0
            command:
            - python
            - run_job.py
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: '2'
                memory: 512Mi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  concurrencyPolicy: Forbid
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,8
1037,"We need a Pod named pdf-generator-pod in default. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. The configuration requires the container identified as main, while also pulling golang:3.1, requesting 2 CPU, authenticated as service account monitoring-sa, and also restarting on Never.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""golang:3.1""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.serviceAccountName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring-sa""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: pdf-generator-pod
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
    env: production
spec:
  restartPolicy: Never
  containers:
  - name: main
    image: golang:3.1
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: '2'
        memory: 1Gi
  serviceAccountName: monitoring-sa",Pod,8
1038,"Please configure a Deployment identified as cache-proxy within ml. Make sure it has having 3 replicated pods, tagged as team=ml, while also built from ruby:14, the container identified as main, while also with Recreate as the strategy type.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
