1040,The web-app-svc Service operates in the logging namespace. It is configured with accessible via port 11211. It requires target port set to 443. It has selecting pods labeled app=image-processor. It requires service type LoadBalancer.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""11211""}]","apiVersion: v1
