1041,"Deploy a Service called data-pipeline-svc in the development namespace. It should have accessible via port 80, with UDP as the transport protocol, additionally as a ClusterIP service, additionally forwarding to target port 15672.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data-pipeline-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}]","apiVersion: v1
