1042,"Spin up an Ingress called image-processor-ingress in the infra namespace. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. It should have directing traffic for the host docs.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""image-processor-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""docs.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
