1045,We need a CronJob named report-gen-cron in monitoring. The configuration requires executing on the 0 0 * * * cron schedule.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 * * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: report-gen-cron
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    env: staging
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
