1047,"Configure a Deployment called batch-processor in the platform namespace. It should have maintaining 1 pods, additionally accepting connections on container port 8080, additionally with a CPU request of 250m, built from centos:1.2, and also naming the container batch-processor.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""centos:1.2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""250m""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: batch-processor
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: batch-processor
    tier: backend
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: batch-processor
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: batch-processor
        tier: backend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: batch-processor
        image: centos:1.2
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8080
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 1Gi",Deployment,8
1048,The ssl-terminator-cron CronJob operates in the platform namespace. It includes keeping 1 failed job(s) in history. It is configured with scheduled at 0 */2 * * *.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */2 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.failedJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: ssl-terminator-cron
  namespace: platform
spec:
  schedule: 0 */2 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: job
            image: golang:latest
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - echo hello
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  failedJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,5
1049,The batch-processor Deployment operates in the default namespace. It has based on the memcached:14 image. It features the container identified as worker. It features running 8 copies.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: batch-processor
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: batch-processor
    tier: frontend
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: batch-processor
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: batch-processor
        tier: frontend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
