          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 2Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,6
1050,"We need a CronJob named analytics-engine-cron in infra. The configuration requires OnFailure restart behavior, and with the cron schedule 0 */6 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""analytics-engine-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */6 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: analytics-engine-cron
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    env: development
spec:
  schedule: 0 */6 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: cron
            image: prom/prometheus:5.0
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  suspend: false
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 5",CronJob,5
1051,"Provision a Deployment called stream-consumer in the default namespace. It should have maintaining 6 pods, additionally with the container labeled main, pulling nats:2.0.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nats:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: stream-consumer
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: stream-consumer
    release: canary
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: stream-consumer
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: stream-consumer
        release: canary
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: nats:2.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 27017
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 512Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always",Deployment,6
1052,"Please configure a Service identified as model-trainer-svc within platform. Make sure it has of type LoadBalancer, while also configured with ClientIP affinity, proxying to port 80 on the backend, while also targeting pods with app=ml-inference, and with UDP as the transport protocol.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""80""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
