1053,"Please configure a Deployment identified as circuit-breaker within production. Make sure it has allocated 2 CPU, the container identified as app, additionally with mysql:stable as the base image, while also with the tier label set to queue, and also with 5 replicas.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""circuit-breaker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql:stable""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""queue""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: circuit-breaker
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: circuit-breaker
    tier: queue
    version: v2
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: circuit-breaker
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: circuit-breaker
        tier: queue
        version: v2
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: mysql:stable
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3306
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 128Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 4Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,8
1054,"Please configure a Service identified as feature-store-svc within staging. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. Make sure it has configured with ClientIP affinity, as a ClusterIP service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
