  sessionAffinity: ClientIP",Service,5
1055,The circuit-breaker-config ConfigMap operates in the platform namespace. It includes including a allowed_origins data key. It requires where the allowed_origins field is https://app.example.com. It includes having the api_key_prefix field. It features having allowed_origins match the substring htt. It requires where the timeout_seconds field is 30.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""circuit-breaker-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""30""}, {""path"": ""data.api_key_prefix"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""htt""}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""https://app.example.com""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: circuit-breaker-config
  namespace: platform
data:
  allowed_origins: https://app.example.com
  api_key_prefix: pk-
  timeout_seconds: '30'",ConfigMap,8
1056,"Set up a Service called queue-worker-svc in the production namespace. It should have forwarding to target port 27017, operating as a NodePort service, using TCP protocol, accepting traffic on port 9000.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""queue-worker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9000""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""27017""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}]","apiVersion: v1
