1057,"Create an Ingress called scheduler-ingress in the default namespace. It should have backed by service catalog-api-svc, bound to host auth.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api-svc""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: scheduler-ingress
  namespace: default
spec:
  rules:
  - host: auth.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /ws
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: catalog-api-svc
            port:
              number: 3000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - auth.example.com
    secretName: scheduler-tls
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,5
1058,The metrics-collector Deployment operates in the default namespace. It features configured with Always pull behavior. It includes naming the container app. It has running mongo:21. It requires deployed via Recreate. It includes a replica count of 6.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongo:21""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Always""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
