1059,"Please configure a Service identified as load-balancer-svc within default. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. Make sure it has accepting traffic on port 9000, targeting pods with app=catalog-api, additionally using ClientIP session affinity, while also of type NodePort, with TCP as the transport protocol.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""load-balancer-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9000""}]","apiVersion: v1
