1065,The event-bus-config ConfigMap operates in the logging namespace. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. It requires where the feature_flags field is dark_mode=false.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dark_mode=false""}]","apiVersion: v1
