1067,The circuit-breaker-svc Service operates in the development namespace. It is configured with session affinity set to ClientIP. It is configured with nodePort 31414. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. It requires of type NodePort.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""circuit-breaker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.nodePort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""31414""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
