1069,"Provision a Deployment called scheduler in the ml namespace. Integration tests for this component run in the CI pipeline on every merge to main. It should have bitnami/kafka:2.0 as its container image, running in a container named server, maintaining 10 pods, and with the env label set to development.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
