1071,"Provision a Deployment called payment-gateway in the ml namespace. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. It should have running 8 copies, pulling minio/minio:5.0, naming the container server, and allocated 128Mi memory.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""minio/minio:5.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""128Mi""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
