1073,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name report-gen-svc, deployed to data. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Specifications include via TCP, operating as a LoadBalancer service, and also accepting traffic on port 5000, targeting pods with app=session-store, additionally proxying to port 5432 on the backend.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5432""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}]","apiVersion: v1
