1074,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name notification-svc-ingress, deployed to default. Specifications include with TLS enabled for host dashboard.example.com, handling traffic for dashboard.example.com, and also on path /admin, listening on port 8080, and with TLS using the secret notification-svc-tls.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dashboard.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.hosts.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dashboard.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/admin""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.secretName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-tls""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
