1078,The backend-ingress Ingress operates in the infra namespace. It has on path /uploads. It requires routing to backend service scheduler-svc. It includes responding to requests for shop.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""shop.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/uploads""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
