1082,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: an Ingress with name gateway-ingress, deployed to ml. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. Specifications include handling traffic for grafana.example.com, forwarding requests to the rate-limiter-svc service, managed by the nginx ingress controller, annotated with ssl-redirect set to true, configured with pathType ImplementationSpecific.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.ingressClassName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nginx""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.ssl-redirect"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ImplementationSpecific""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
