spec:
  rules:
  - host: grafana.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /
        pathType: ImplementationSpecific
        backend:
          service:
            name: rate-limiter-svc
            port:
              number: 8080
  ingressClassName: nginx",Ingress,8
1083,"Configure a CronJob called stream-consumer-cron in the logging namespace. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. It should have scheduled at 0 0 1 * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 0 1 * *""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: stream-consumer-cron
  namespace: logging
spec:
  schedule: 0 0 1 * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: runner
            image: node:17
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 500m
                memory: 256Mi
          restartPolicy: OnFailure",CronJob,4
1084,The frontend Deployment operates in the production namespace. It has serving on container port 8443. It includes allocated 1 CPU. It requires whose container is called worker. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. It includes running 5 copies. It includes built from vault:14.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8443""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: frontend
  namespace: production
  labels:
    app: frontend
    release: canary
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: frontend
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: frontend
        release: canary
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: vault:14
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 512Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always
        env:
        - name: DEBUG
          value: 'false'",Deployment,8
1085,Spin up a ConfigMap called notification-svc-config in the infra namespace. It should have where debug_mode contains tru.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""notification-svc-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""data.debug_mode"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""tru""}]","apiVersion: v1
