1087,The ml-inference-pod Pod operates in the data namespace. It is configured with rabbitmq:16 as the base image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rabbitmq:16""}]","apiVersion: v1
