1089,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name feature-store-svc, deployed to development. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. Specifications include of type ClusterIP.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""feature-store-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}]","apiVersion: v1
