1090,The worker-cron CronJob operates in the infra namespace. It includes based on the ubuntu:4.0 image. It features set to fire at */5 * * * *. It requires requesting 50m CPU. It is configured with its command starting with /bin/sh. It includes restart policy Never.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""*/5 * * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ubuntu:4.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50m""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.command.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/bin/sh""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: worker-cron
  namespace: infra
spec:
  schedule: '*/5 * * * *'
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: task
            image: ubuntu:4.0
            command:
            - /bin/sh
            - -c
            - date; echo done
            resources:
              requests:
                cpu: 50m
                memory: 1Gi
          restartPolicy: Never",CronJob,8
1091,"Please configure a ConfigMap identified as event-bus-config within production. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Make sure it has where app_env contains pro, having workers=8 in its data, and containing rate_limit set to 100.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""data.workers"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""data.rate_limit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""100""}, {""path"": ""data.app_env"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""pro""}]","apiVersion: v1
