1092,The inventory-svc-svc Service operates in the platform namespace. It includes via TCP. It has target port set to 8500. It includes selecting pods labeled app=session-store. It has sticky sessions via ClientIP. It requires configured as LoadBalancer.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.sessionAffinity"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClientIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""session-store""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8500""}]","apiVersion: v1
