1099,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name worker-config, deployed to platform. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Specifications include where the app_port field is 5000, where app_name contains sch, storing retry_count with value 3, while also carrying label team: data, and with a feature_flags entry present.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""sch""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}, {""path"": ""data.retry_count"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}]","apiVersion: v1
