1100,The webhook-relay Deployment operates in the ml namespace. It includes including REDIS_URL in its environment. It has built from prom/prometheus:alpine. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. It has naming the container main. It includes running 5 copies.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""REDIS_URL""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: webhook-relay
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: webhook-relay
    release: green
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: webhook-relay
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: webhook-relay
        release: green
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: prom/prometheus:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9200
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 4Gi
        env:
        - name: REDIS_URL
          value: 'false'",Deployment,7
1101,"Spin up an Ingress called report-gen-ingress in the data namespace. It should have serving grafana.example.com, capturing requests to /static, additionally forwarding requests to the audit-logger-svc service, and also using pathType Prefix.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""report-gen-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""grafana.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/static""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: report-gen-ingress
  namespace: data
  annotations:
    rewrite-target: 50m
spec:
  rules:
  - host: grafana.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /static
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: audit-logger-svc
            port:
              number: 80",Ingress,7
1102,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name cdn-origin, deployed to monitoring. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Specifications include employing RollingUpdate for deployments, having 6 replicated pods, based on the openjdk:latest image, running in a container named worker, and allocated 1Gi memory.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""openjdk:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1Gi""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cdn-origin
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: cdn-origin
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cdn-origin
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cdn-origin
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: openjdk:latest
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 256Mi",Deployment,8
1103,"Please configure an Ingress identified as web-app-ingress within default. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. Make sure it has the env label set to production, while also listening on port 443, and also directing traffic for the host ws.example.com, additionally employing ImplementationSpecific path matching, while also matching /docs.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ws.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ImplementationSpecific""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/docs""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
