        - name: SECRET_KEY
          value: '60'",Deployment,6
1108,"Set up an Ingress called catalog-api-ingress in the data namespace. It should have the catalog-api-tls TLS secret, with path matching set to Prefix, accessible via port 5000, directing traffic for the host cdn.example.com, and carrying annotation rewrite-target: /.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.rewrite-target"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.secretName"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api-tls""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: catalog-api-ingress
  namespace: data
  annotations:
    rewrite-target: /
spec:
  rules:
  - host: cdn.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /api/v1
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: stream-consumer-svc
            port:
              number: 5000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - cdn.example.com
    secretName: catalog-api-tls",Ingress,8
1109,"Please configure a ConfigMap identified as order-service-config within data. Make sure it has containing max_connections set to 100, which includes a cache_ttl key, containing the max_connections entry, and also storing workers with value 2, containing cache_ttl set to 600.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""order-service-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.workers"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""600""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""100""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: order-service-config
  namespace: data
data:
  cache_ttl: '600'
  max_connections: '100'
  workers: '2'
  rate_limit: '500'",ConfigMap,8
1110,"Spin up a Deployment called model-trainer in the data namespace. It should have its container called app, using ubuntu:latest as its container image, accepting connections on container port 9090, and running 2 copies.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ubuntu:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: model-trainer
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: model-trainer
    version: v1.0
    team: ml
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: model-trainer
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: model-trainer
        version: v1.0
        team: ml
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: ubuntu:latest
        ports:
        - containerPort: 9090
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 512Mi
        env:
        - name: SECRET_KEY
          value: '8080'",Deployment,7
1111,"We need a Deployment named web-app in logging. The configuration requires naming the container server, pulling nginx:1.2, with a replica count of 5, additionally with container port 4222.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""nginx:1.2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: web-app
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: web-app
    tier: queue
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: web-app
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: web-app
        tier: queue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: nginx:1.2
        ports:
        - containerPort: 4222
        env:
        - name: REDIS_URL
          value: info",Deployment,7
1112,"Spin up a Deployment called gateway in the logging namespace. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. It should have maintaining 8 pods, naming the container app, running mysql:17.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""gateway""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql:17""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: gateway
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: gateway
    team: data
spec:
  replicas: 8
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: gateway
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: gateway
        team: data
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: mysql:17
        ports:
        - containerPort: 15672
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 128Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 200m
            memory: 512Mi",Deployment,6
1113,The file-uploader-ingress Ingress operates in the monitoring namespace. It has employing Prefix path matching. It features bound to host beta.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: file-uploader-ingress
  namespace: monitoring
  annotations:
    description: Ingress for file-uploader-ingress
spec:
  rules:
  - host: beta.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /health
        pathType: Prefix
