1114,Configure a Pod called frontend-pod in the ml namespace. It should have rabbitmq:3.9 as its container image.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rabbitmq:3.9""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
