1119,"Configure a Deployment called web-app in the development namespace. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. It should have pulling ruby:20, and also the container identified as app, and with 2 replicas.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ruby:20""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
