1123,"We need a Deployment named backend in staging. The configuration requires ubuntu:2.0 as the base image, additionally maintaining 10 pods, and whose container is called main.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ubuntu:2.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
