1124,The ml-inference-config ConfigMap operates in the infra namespace. It features which includes a app_name key. It has app_name containing the text log. It is configured with mapping app_name to log-aggregator. It is configured with feature_flags configured as beta=true.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""beta=true""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""log-aggregator""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""log""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
