  log_level: info
  retry_count: '3'
  rate_limit: '1000'",ConfigMap,7
1125,The metrics-collector-config ConfigMap operates in the monitoring namespace.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}]","apiVersion: v1
