    targetPort: 9000
    protocol: UDP",Service,8
1127,The inventory-svc-svc Service operates in the logging namespace. It features via UDP. Rollback procedures for this deployment are documented in the runbook. It includes targeting port 443. Related services include the auth-proxy and rate-limiter deployments in the same namespace. It has set up as ClusterIP.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""443""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: inventory-svc-svc
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: inventory
    env: production
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  selector:
    app: metrics-collector
  ports:
  - port: 443
    targetPort: 443
    protocol: UDP",Service,6
1128,The api-server-svc Service operates in the data namespace. It has routing to backend port 9000. It has accepting traffic on port 9090. It has of type LoadBalancer. It features targeting pods with app=api-server.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9000""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: api-server-svc
  namespace: data
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: api-server
  ports:
  - port: 9090
    targetPort: 9000
    protocol: UDP",Service,7
1129,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name api-server, deployed to staging. Specifications include scaled to 10 instances, while also with the container labeled main, while also tagged as release=blue, and also using vault:alpine as its container image, allocated 50m CPU.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""vault:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.release"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""blue""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.cpu"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50m""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: api-server
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: api-server
    release: blue
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: api-server
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: api-server
        release: blue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: vault:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 3000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 1Gi
          limits:
            cpu: '1'
            memory: 256Mi
        imagePullPolicy: Always",Deployment,8
1130,"Please configure a Deployment identified as worker within monitoring. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. Make sure it has a replica count of 4, running kibana:alpine, and naming the container server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""kibana:alpine""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: worker
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    app: worker
    env: production
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: worker
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: worker
        env: production
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: kibana:alpine
        ports:
        - containerPort: 6379
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 512Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 1000m
            memory: 512Mi
        env:
        - name: LOG_LEVEL
          value: info",Deployment,6
1131,"We need a Service named health-checker-svc in default. The configuration requires operating on TCP, and also with target port set to 4222, while also operating as a LoadBalancer service, accessible via port 5432, annotated with env=development.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5432""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: health-checker-svc
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: health-checker
    env: development
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: load-balancer
  ports:
  - port: 5432
    targetPort: 4222
    protocol: TCP",Service,8
1132,"We need an Ingress named worker-ingress in infra. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. The configuration requires capturing requests to /health, bound to host auth.example.com, with port 8080 open, with path matching set to Prefix, and carrying annotation description: /.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.pathType"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Prefix""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.backend.service.port.number"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.http.paths.0.path"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/health""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.description"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""/""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: worker-ingress
  namespace: infra
  annotations:
    description: /
  labels:
    env: production
spec:
  rules:
  - host: auth.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /health
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: log-aggregator-svc
            port:
              number: 8080
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - auth.example.com
    secretName: worker-tls",Ingress,8
1133,"Please configure a Service identified as service-mesh-svc within monitoring. Make sure it has set up as ClusterIP, forwarding traffic to pods with app=cache-proxy, using TCP protocol, and serving on port 8080.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""service-mesh-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}]","apiVersion: v1
