1134,"We need a Deployment named batch-processor in ml. The SLA for this service requires 99.95% uptime. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. The configuration requires elasticsearch:5.0 as its container image, additionally configuring the METRICS_PORT variable, with imagePullPolicy set to Never, running 1 copies, and running in a container named app.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""elasticsearch:5.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.imagePullPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Never""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""METRICS_PORT""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: batch-processor
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: batch-processor
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: batch-processor
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: batch-processor
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: elasticsearch:5.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 1883
        imagePullPolicy: Never
        env:
        - name: METRICS_PORT
          value: '8080'",Deployment,8
1135,"Please configure a Service identified as email-sender-svc within ml. Make sure it has targeting pods with app=event-bus, additionally with UDP as the transport protocol, and as a ClusterIP service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""event-bus""}]","apiVersion: v1
