          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 4Gi
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,7
1137,The api-server Deployment operates in the logging namespace. Performance benchmarks show this configuration handles 500 concurrent connections comfortably. It requires container port 5000. It has openjdk:1.2 as its container image. It features the container should share the same name as the resource itself. It has scaled to 2 instances. It requires requesting 256Mi of memory.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""openjdk:1.2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""api-server""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""256Mi""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: api-server
  namespace: logging
  labels:
    app: api-server
    release: stable
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: api-server
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: api-server
        release: stable
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: api-server
        image: openjdk:1.2
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 100m
            memory: 256Mi
        env:
        - name: DATABASE_URL
          value: '8080'",Deployment,8
1138,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name ssl-terminator-config, deployed to staging. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Specifications include mapping allowed_origins to https://app.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""data.allowed_origins"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""https://app.example.com""}]","apiVersion: v1
