1139,"We need a Service named analytics-engine-svc in platform. The configuration requires communicating over UDP, with service type NodePort, additionally exposed externally on port 31607, while also carrying label env: production, and exposing port 4222.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""analytics-engine-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.nodePort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""31607""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""UDP""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}]","apiVersion: v1
