1142,The stream-consumer-config ConfigMap operates in the default namespace. It is configured with where the debug_mode field is true. It has a debug_mode entry present. It features having app_name=cache-proxy in its data. It includes containing feature_flags set to dark_mode=false. It requires rate_limit configured as 100.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""stream-consumer-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""data.rate_limit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""100""}, {""path"": ""data.debug_mode"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""data.feature_flags"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dark_mode=false""}, {""path"": ""data.debug_mode"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}]","apiVersion: v1
