1145,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name health-checker, deployed to production. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. Specifications include with the container labeled worker, with 4 replicas, built from mongo:slim, and deployed via RollingUpdate.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongo:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
