        ports:
        - containerPort: 11211",Deployment,7
1146,"Configure a Deployment called cache-proxy in the infra namespace. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. It should have the container identified as server, built from alpine:14, and also scaled to 10 instances.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""alpine:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: cache-proxy
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    app: cache-proxy
    release: blue
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: cache-proxy
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: cache-proxy
        release: blue
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: alpine:14
        ports:
        - containerPort: 1883
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: '2'
            memory: 512Mi
        env:
        - name: DATABASE_URL
          value: '60'",Deployment,6
1147,"Please configure a Deployment identified as file-uploader within staging. Note that this resource may be scaled horizontally during high-traffic events. Make sure it has based on the python:1.0 image, scaled to 10 instances, and naming the container server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""file-uploader""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: file-uploader
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: file-uploader
spec:
  replicas: 10
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: file-uploader
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
