1150,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name model-trainer, deployed to development. Specifications include having 6 replicated pods, with container port 5432, with its container called app, running bitnami/kafka:3.9, and with env var METRICS_PORT assigned to true.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""model-trainer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""development""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""bitnami/kafka:3.9""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5432""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""true""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: model-trainer
  namespace: development
  labels:
    app: model-trainer
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: model-trainer
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: model-trainer
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
