    protocol: TCP",Service,6
1168,The health-checker-svc Service operates in the logging namespace. It features matching pods carrying app=metrics-collector. It features proxying to port 3000 on the backend. It has port 15672 open. It features service type ClusterIP. It has the team label set to frontend.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""frontend""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3000""}]","apiVersion: v1
