1170,The web-app-svc Service operates in the staging namespace. It has set up as ClusterIP. It is configured with target port set to 1883. It is configured with targeting pods with app=webhook-relay.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""web-app-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ClusterIP""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1883""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""webhook-relay""}]","apiVersion: v1
