1171,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a CronJob with name worker-cron, deployed to infra. Specifications include running in a container named worker, restarting on OnFailure, while also carrying label team: backend, retaining 1 successful job records, and running on schedule 0 */2 * * *.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""CronJob""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker-cron""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.schedule"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""0 */2 * * *""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.jobTemplate.spec.template.spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.team"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""backend""}, {""path"": ""spec.successfulJobsHistoryLimit"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1""}]","apiVersion: batch/v1
kind: CronJob
metadata:
  name: worker-cron
  namespace: infra
  labels:
    team: backend
spec:
  schedule: 0 */2 * * *
  jobTemplate:
    spec:
      template:
        spec:
          containers:
          - name: worker
            image: node:17
          restartPolicy: OnFailure
  successfulJobsHistoryLimit: 1",CronJob,8
