1174,"Please configure a ConfigMap identified as inventory-svc-config within platform. Make sure it has having cache_ttl=3600 in its data, additionally with cache_ttl containing the text 360.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3600""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""360""}]","apiVersion: v1
