1175,The rate-limiter Deployment operates in the data namespace. It includes a replica count of 2. It requires openjdk:1.0 as the base image. It requires the container identified as worker. It is configured with environment variable CACHE_TTL=8080.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""2""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""openjdk:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: rate-limiter
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: rate-limiter
    release: stable
    tier: queue
    version: v2.1
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: rate-limiter
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: rate-limiter
        release: stable
        tier: queue
        version: v2.1
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: openjdk:1.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 512Mi
        env:
        - name: CACHE_TTL
          value: '8080'",Deployment,7
1176,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name cdn-origin-svc, deployed to data. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. Expected traffic volume is approximately 10,000 requests per second during peak hours. Specifications include as a LoadBalancer service.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}]","apiVersion: v1
