    targetPort: 9090
    protocol: TCP",Service,4
1177,"Provision a Pod called payment-gateway-pod in the staging namespace. It should have built from redis:latest, the container identified as server, and with the tier label set to cache.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""payment-gateway-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""redis:latest""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.tier"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: v1
