1178,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name cache-proxy-config, deployed to staging. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. Specifications include mapping app_port to 3000, having app_port match the substring 300, with app_env configured as production, where the app_env entry includes pro.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cache-proxy-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""data.app_env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""300""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""3000""}, {""path"": ""data.app_env"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""pro""}]","apiVersion: v1
