1180,"We need a ConfigMap named inventory-svc-config in monitoring. The configuration requires including a log_level data key, containing app_port set to 9090.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""data.app_port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""9090""}, {""path"": ""data.log_level"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
