1181,The scheduler Deployment operates in the data namespace. It features a Recreate rollout strategy. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Documentation for this component is maintained in the team wiki under infrastructure/configs. It requires 6 replicas. It features running traefik:slim. It features the container identified as worker.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""scheduler""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""6""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""traefik:slim""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: scheduler
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: scheduler
spec:
  replicas: 6
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: scheduler
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: scheduler
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: traefik:slim
        ports:
        - containerPort: 5000
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 512Mi",Deployment,7
1182,"We need a Service named queue-worker-svc in platform. The associated monitoring dashboard is available on Grafana. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. The configuration requires as a NodePort service, proxying to port 8080 on the backend, matching pods carrying app=catalog-api, and with nodePort 31806.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""queue-worker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""catalog-api""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.nodePort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""31806""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8080""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: queue-worker-svc
  namespace: platform
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: catalog-api
  ports:
  - port: 9000
    targetPort: 8080
    protocol: UDP
    nodePort: 31806",Service,7
1183,Please configure an Ingress identified as rate-limiter-ingress within production. Make sure it has bound to host ws.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""rate-limiter-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ws.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: rate-limiter-ingress
  namespace: production
  annotations:
    description: Ingress for rate-limiter-ingress
spec:
  rules:
  - host: ws.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: log-aggregator-svc
            port:
              number: 3000
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - ws.example.com
    secretName: rate-limiter-tls",Ingress,4
1184,The ssl-terminator Deployment operates in the staging namespace. It has naming the container worker. It is configured with running minio/minio:1.0. It is configured with having 4 replicated pods.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ssl-terminator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""minio/minio:1.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: ssl-terminator
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: ssl-terminator
    release: canary
    version: v2
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: ssl-terminator
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: ssl-terminator
        release: canary
        version: v2
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: minio/minio:1.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8443
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 4Gi
          limits:
            cpu: 50m
            memory: 1Gi",Deployment,6
1185,"Spin up a ConfigMap called ml-inference-config in the ml namespace. It should have containing the app_name entry, storing app_name with value metrics-collector, with a max_connections entry present, containing timeout_seconds set to 10, with debug_mode containing the text tru.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""data.timeout_seconds"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""10""}, {""path"": ""data.debug_mode"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""tru""}, {""path"": ""data.max_connections"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector""}, {""path"": ""data.app_name"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: ml-inference-config
  namespace: ml
data:
  app_name: metrics-collector
  max_connections: '10'
  debug_mode: 'true'
  timeout_seconds: '10'
  workers: '1'
  rate_limit: '100'",ConfigMap,8
1186,"Configure an Ingress called dns-resolver-ingress in the platform namespace. This service was originally implemented in the monolith and is now being extracted as a microservice. It should have including the rewrite-target=50m annotation, with TLS termination on v2.api.example.com, and serving v2.api.example.com.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""dns-resolver-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""v2.api.example.com""}, {""path"": ""spec.tls.0.hosts.0"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""v2.api.example.com""}, {""path"": ""metadata.annotations.rewrite-target"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""50m""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: dns-resolver-ingress
  namespace: platform
  annotations:
    rewrite-target: 50m
spec:
  rules:
  - host: v2.api.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /ws
        pathType: Prefix
        backend:
          service:
            name: audit-logger-svc
            port:
              number: 80
  tls:
  - hosts:
    - v2.api.example.com
    secretName: dns-resolver-tls
  ingressClassName: haproxy",Ingress,6
1187,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a ConfigMap with name cdn-origin-config, deployed to ml. This configuration supersedes the legacy setup that was decommissioned last quarter. Feature flags controlling this service are managed through LaunchDarkly. Specifications include containing the cache_ttl entry, and also with the app_env value including pro, having cache_ttl=600 in its data.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""cdn-origin-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml""}, {""path"": ""data.app_env"", ""operator"": ""contains"", ""value"": ""pro""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""600""}, {""path"": ""data.cache_ttl"", ""operator"": ""exists"", ""value"": """"}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: cdn-origin-config
  namespace: ml
  labels:
    app: analytics-engine
data:
  cache_ttl: '600'
  app_env: production",ConfigMap,6
1188,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Service with name health-checker-svc, deployed to default. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Specifications include set up as LoadBalancer, and also forwarding to target port 5000, and selecting pods labeled app=audit-logger.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""health-checker-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""audit-logger""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: health-checker-svc
  namespace: default
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: audit-logger
  ports:
  - port: 80
    targetPort: 5000
    protocol: TCP",Service,6
1189,We need a ConfigMap named pdf-generator-config in staging.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ConfigMap""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator-config""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}]","apiVersion: v1
