  name: pdf-generator-config
  namespace: staging
data:
  retry_count: '3'
  app_env: staging",ConfigMap,3
1190,Please configure an Ingress identified as email-sender-ingress within monitoring. Capacity planning documents suggest this workload will double by end of year. Ensure this configuration is reviewed by the security team before deployment. Make sure it has bound to host ws.example.com.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""email-sender-ingress""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""monitoring""}, {""path"": ""spec.rules.0.host"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ws.example.com""}]","apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: email-sender-ingress
  namespace: monitoring
  labels:
    env: testing
spec:
  rules:
  - host: ws.example.com
    http:
      paths:
      - path: /static
        pathType: Exact
        backend:
          service:
            name: image-processor-svc
            port:
              number: 5000
  ingressClassName: haproxy",Ingress,4
1191,The search-engine-pod Pod operates in the staging namespace. It has pulling memcached:16.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""search-engine-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""memcached:16""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: search-engine-pod
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: search-engine
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: server
    image: memcached:16",Pod,4
1192,"Please configure a Service identified as load-balancer-svc within infra. Make sure it has as a NodePort service, forwarding traffic to pods with app=inventory-svc, with port 8443 open, routing to backend port 15672, and using TCP protocol.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""load-balancer-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""infra""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8443""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.protocol"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""TCP""}, {""path"": ""spec.selector.app"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""inventory-svc""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.targetPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""15672""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: load-balancer-svc
  namespace: infra
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: inventory-svc
  ports:
  - port: 8443
    targetPort: 15672
    protocol: TCP",Service,8
1193,"We need a Deployment named auth-service in staging. The configuration requires running 5 copies, while also whose container is called app, while also built from logstash:14, additionally opening container port 8200, with the env label set to testing.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""auth-service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logstash:14""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""app""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""testing""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""8200""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: auth-service
  namespace: staging
  labels:
    app: auth-service
    team: frontend
    env: testing
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: auth-service
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: auth-service
        team: frontend
        env: testing
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: logstash:14
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8200
        imagePullPolicy: Never",Deployment,8
1194,Please configure a Service identified as user-service-svc within logging. The data processed by this service is classified as PII and must comply with GDPR requirements. The on-call rotation for this service follows the standard PagerDuty schedule. Make sure it has service type LoadBalancer.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""user-service-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""logging""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""LoadBalancer""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: user-service-svc
  namespace: logging
spec:
  type: LoadBalancer
  selector:
    app: catalog-api
  ports:
  - port: 15672
    targetPort: 3000
    protocol: UDP",Service,4
1195,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name batch-processor, deployed to data. Specifications include scaled to 4 instances, with Recreate as the strategy type, pulling mysql:3.0, and also with its container called main.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""batch-processor""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""data""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mysql:3.0""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""main""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Recreate""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: batch-processor
  namespace: data
  labels:
    app: batch-processor
    tier: backend
    env: production
spec:
  replicas: 4
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: batch-processor
  strategy:
    type: Recreate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: batch-processor
        tier: backend
        env: production
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: main
        image: mysql:3.0
        ports:
        - containerPort: 8500
        imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent",Deployment,7
1196,"Configure the following Kubernetes resource: a Deployment with name load-balancer, deployed to default. This component is part of the Q3 platform migration project. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. Specifications include pulling mongo:8, with a replica count of 5, and with the container labeled server.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""load-balancer""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""default""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""mongo:8""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""server""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: load-balancer
  namespace: default
  labels:
    app: load-balancer
    env: production
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: load-balancer
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: load-balancer
        env: production
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: server
        image: mongo:8
        ports:
        - containerPort: 1883
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 750m
            memory: 128Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 2Gi",Deployment,6
1197,"We need a Deployment named pdf-generator in platform. The configuration requires running 5 copies, based on the python:latest image, the container identified as worker, opening container port 4222, with RollingUpdate as the strategy type.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Deployment""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""pdf-generator""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.replicas"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""python:latest""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""worker""}, {""path"": ""spec.strategy.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""RollingUpdate""}, {""path"": ""spec.template.spec.containers.0.ports.0.containerPort"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""4222""}]","apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: pdf-generator
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: pdf-generator
    release: stable
    team: frontend
spec:
  replicas: 5
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: pdf-generator
  strategy:
    type: RollingUpdate
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: pdf-generator
        release: stable
        team: frontend
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: worker
        image: python:latest
        ports:
        - containerPort: 4222
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: 500m
            memory: 512Mi
          limits:
            cpu: 250m
            memory: 256Mi
        env:
        - name: DEBUG
          value: '60'",Deployment,8
1198,The metrics-collector-svc Service operates in the production namespace. It has of type NodePort. It features accessible via port 5000.,"[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Service""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""metrics-collector-svc""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""production""}, {""path"": ""spec.type"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""NodePort""}, {""path"": ""spec.ports.0.port"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""5000""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: metrics-collector-svc
  namespace: production
spec:
  type: NodePort
  selector:
    app: cdn-origin
  ports:
  - port: 5000
    targetPort: 11211
    protocol: UDP
    nodePort: 31380",Service,5
1199,"Set up a Pod called ml-inference-pod in the platform namespace. Cost allocation for this resource falls under the platform-infrastructure budget category. The team responsible for this resource can be reached via the platform-ops Slack channel. It should have NODE_ENV configured as info, additionally tagged as env=staging, with a restart policy of OnFailure, reserving 1Gi of memory, and also with prom/prometheus:3.9 as the base image.","[{""path"": ""kind"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""Pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.name"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""ml-inference-pod""}, {""path"": ""metadata.namespace"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""platform""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.image"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""prom/prometheus:3.9""}, {""path"": ""metadata.labels.env"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""staging""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.env.0.value"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""info""}, {""path"": ""spec.containers.0.resources.requests.memory"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""1Gi""}, {""path"": ""spec.restartPolicy"", ""operator"": ""equals"", ""value"": ""OnFailure""}]","apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: ml-inference-pod
  namespace: platform
  labels:
    app: ml-inference
    env: staging
spec:
  restartPolicy: OnFailure
  containers:
  - name: server
    image: prom/prometheus:3.9
    resources:
      requests:
        cpu: 200m
        memory: 1Gi
    env:
    - name: NODE_ENV
      value: info
    imagePullPolicy: Always",Pod,8
